(308, NULL, 11, 55, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Beautiful red Jimme choo sharee with pearl and stone work', 'I-000007', 'productImages/otEZ81710133151.jpg', '[\"17101331526dASW.jpg\",\"1710133152GYhbQ.jpg\",\"1710133152PUeRB.jpg\",\"1712563866w68O3.jpg\"]', 'Beautiful red Jimme Choo Sharee boasts exquisite pearl and stone work, adding a touch of opulence to your ensemble. Perfect for those seeking timeless elegance with a hint of luxury.', '<p>Introducing the stunning &quot;Ruby Elegance&quot; Jimme Choo sharee, a masterpiece that seamlessly blends traditional allure with contemporary finesse. Crafted with the finest attention to detail, this sharee embodies timeless grace and sophistication.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The sharee is crafted from luxurious red jimme choo&nbsp;fabric, renowned for its lustrous sheen and smooth texture, which gracefully drapes around the body, accentuating every movement with elegance. Adorning the sharee are exquisite pearl and stone embellishments, meticulously handcrafted to add a touch of opulence and sparkle to the ensemble. The pearls delicately shimmer against the rich red backdrop, while the intricate stone work adds depth and dimension, creating a mesmerizing visual feast.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The border of the sharee is adorned with intricate patterns of pearls and stones, cascading down the length of the drape, framing it with unparalleled beauty. The pallu is adorned with elaborate motifs, featuring a harmonious blend of pearls and stones arranged in a captivating design, adding a regal touch to the attire.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Accompanying this resplendent sharee is a matching blouse piece, meticulously designed to complement the saree perfectly. Crafted from the same luxurious jimme choo&nbsp;fabric, it features delicate pearl and stone embellishments along the neckline and sleeves, enhancing its allure and completing the ensemble with finesse.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Whether it&#39;s a wedding celebration, a festive occasion, or an elegant evening soiree, the &quot;Ruby Elegance&quot; Jimme Choo sharee is sure to make a statement wherever you go. With its exquisite craftsmanship, luxurious fabric, and timeless design, it exudes sophistication and charm, leaving a lasting impression on all who behold it. Embrace the allure of tradition with a contemporary twist and make a dazzling entrance in this breathtaking masterpiece.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Fabric: </strong>Jimme&nbsp;Choo</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Aanchal: </strong>Same as Sharee Color&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Blouse:&nbsp;</strong>With Blouse Piece</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, 8500, 7500, 0, 1, 1, 'saree,sare,party sharee,indian sharee,jimme choo sharee,pearl work sharee,stone work sharee,fashionable share,red sharee', NULL, NULL, 'beautiful-red-jimme-choo-sharee-with-pearl-and-stone-work-1710133152Ll4Wt', 8, 0, NULL, 'Beautiful red Jimme choo sharee with pearl and stone work', 'saree,Bollywood share,party sharee,elegant sharee,treanding share,indian sharee,sharee,gorgeous sharee,stone work sharee,red sharee', 'Elevate your style with our Jimme Choo pearl stone-worked sharee.\r\nPerfect for special occasions.', 1, 0, 0, '2024-03-11 02:59:12', '2024-06-25 07:54:26'),
(309, NULL, 11, 63, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Beautiful Emerald green  color butterfly gown', NULL, 'productImages/RqS1V1710139169.jpg', '[\"1710139170znvoS.jpg\",\"1710139170P7pcO.jpg\",\"1710139171aKkO2.jpg\",\"1712563777d2vp0.jpg\"]', 'Captivate in this stunning emerald green butterfly gown, adorned with intricate stone work delicately embellishing the upper part. The vibrant hue and elegant design make it a mesmerizing choice for any special occasion.\"', '<p>This enchanting gown embodies elegance and grace, crafted to captivate the eye and inspire wonder. The luxurious emerald green fabric cascades like a gentle waterfall, pooling elegantly at the feet of the wearer. The color is reminiscent of lush forests and precious gemstones, exuding a sense of opulence and allure.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The upper part of the gown is a masterpiece of craftsmanship, adorned with intricate stone work that shimmers and dances in the light.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The bodice of the gown is designed to flatter, with a sweetheart neckline that frames the d&eacute;colletage and draws the eye upwards. The silhouette is sculpted to perfection, with expert tailoring ensuring a flawless fit. Soft, sheer fabric drapes gracefully over the shoulders, adding a touch of ethereal romance to the ensemble.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As the eye travels downwards, the skirt of the gown unfurls like the wings of a butterfly, flowing with effortless grace and movement.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At the back, the gown features exquisite detailing, with perhaps a low-cut or illusion back adorned with more intricate stone work. A row of delicate buttons trails down the spine, adding a final touch of sophistication to the design.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This emerald green butterfly gown is not just a garment, but a work of art&mdash;a symbol of beauty, femininity, and enchantment. From the intricate stone work to the flowing silhouette, every detail is designed to dazzle and delight, ensuring that all eyes are on the wearer from the moment she enters the room.