(310, NULL, 11, 55, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Enchanting Elegance: Peacock Blue Shaded Sharee Embellished with Exquisite Stone Work', 'I-000131', 'productImages/Xzd581710140691.jpg', '[\"1710140691Z77n5.jpg\",\"1710140692fdgpt.jpg\",\"1710140692KUmEd.jpg\",\"1710140693LB801.jpg\",\"1712563842RLiMS.jpg\"]', 'Exquisite peacock blue shaded saree adorned with stunning stone work, a perfect blend of elegance and allure.\"', '<p>Indulge in the splendor of nature&#39;s palette with this breathtaking peacock blue shaded saree, a celestial marvel that captures the essence of elegance and grace. The rich hues of azure and teal blend seamlessly, reminiscent of the iridescent plumage of the majestic peacock, evoking a sense of regal splendor and timeless beauty with elaborate designs that mimic the intricate patterns and vibrant colors of this iconic bird. Each stone is carefully selected and expertly placed, creating a mosaic of texture and light that elevates the saree to a work of art.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The blouse that accompanies the sharee is equally resplendent, adorned with matching stone work that complements the design of the sharee. Whether it&#39;s a traditional full-sleeved blouse or a modern halter neck, the blouse adds the perfect finishing touch to this enchanting ensemble.</p>', '<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Fabric: </strong>Jimme Choo</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Aanchal: </strong>Same as Sharee Color&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Blouse:&nbsp;</strong>With Blouse Piece</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, 4500, 3500, 0, 1, 1, 'jimme choo sharee,stone work sharee,peacock blue color sharee,party sharee,fashionable sharee', NULL, NULL, 'enchanting-elegance-peacock-blue-shaded-sharee-embellished-with-exquisite-stone-work-1710140691pLStV', 8, 0, NULL, 'Enchanting Elegance: Peacock Blue Shaded Sharee Embellished with Exquisite Stone Work', 'jimme choo sharee,party sharee, fashionable sharee,stone work sharee,peacock color sharee', 'Exquisite peacock blue shaded saree adorned with stunning stone work, a perfect