(332, NULL, 11, 56, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Retro Fashion Set Women\'s Summer Loose Short T-Shirt + High Waist Long Pants', 'LD-0030', 'productImages/tdh2r1710661011.jpg', NULL, 'Fabric Type : Cotton/ polyester\r\n\r\nThis Retro Fashion Set for Women, perfect for the sunny days of summer! Crafted from high-quality polyester fabric, this set features a loose-fitting short T-shirt paired with high-waisted long pants. The short T-shirt offers a relaxed and breezy feel, while the high-waisted design of the pants elongates the silhouette for a flattering look. Embrace retro vibes with this chic ensemble, ideal for casual outings, beach days, or stylish gatherings under the sun.\r\n\r\nDelivery time: 15-25 days', '<p><strong>Loose Short T-Shirt:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The centerpiece of this ensemble is the loose short t-shirt, designed for both style and ease. With its relaxed fit and breathable fabric, it ensures utmost comfort even on the hottest days. The retro-inspired design features playful patterns, bold colors, or perhaps a quirky graphic, evoking the spirit of bygone eras while maintaining a modern edge.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>High Waist Long Pants:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Complementing the laid-back vibe of the t-shirt, the high waist long pants offer a sleek and sophisticated silhouette. The high-rise design cinches at the waist, accentuating your curves and elongating your legs for a flattering look. Crafted from lightweight, airy fabric, these pants flow gracefully with every step, ensuring unrestricted movement and comfort throughout the day. Whether adorned with retro prints, bold stripes, or a solid hue, these pants add a touch of vintage allure to your summer wardrobe.</p>', NULL, NULL, 2570, 0, 0, 0, 1, 'trendy wear,summer collection,summer wear,fashionable summer wear', NULL, NULL, 'retro-fashion-set-womens-summer-loose-short-tshirt-high-waist-long-pants-17106610111jgg4', 7, 0, NULL, 'Retro Fashion Set Women\'s Summer Loose Short T-Shirt + High Waist Long Pants', 'trendy wear,summer wear,trendy summer wear,fashionable summer wear', 'Embrace the spirit of retro fashion with this charming summer set, combining comfort, style, and a hint of nostalgia.', 1, 1, 0, '2024-03-17 05:36:51', '2024-04-23 03:02:23'),
(333, NULL, 11, 56, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Holiday Style Sling Tube Top Female Wavy Pit Strip Crop Top High Waist Wide Leg Pants Women Fashion Two Piece Set', 'LD-0031', 'productImages/hLByq1710663479.jpg', NULL, 'Fabric Type: Polyester\r\n\r\nGet ready to turn heads with our Holiday Style Sling Tube Top and Wide Leg Pants Two-Piece Set! Crafted from high-quality polyester fabric, this set combines comfort with style effortlessly. The sling tube top features a wavy pit strip design, adding a trendy twist to a classic silhouette. Paired with high-waisted wide-leg pants, this ensemble offers a flattering fit while exuding elegance and sophistication. Perfect for a day out with friends or a special occasion, this two-piece set is a must-have in every fashion-forward woman\'s wardrobe.\r\n\r\nDelivery time: 15-25 days.', '<ol>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Sling Tube Top:</strong> This is a type of top that typically has one strap or a sling-style design over one shoulder, leaving the other shoulder bare. It&#39;s often form-fitting and can vary in length, but in this case, it seems to be a crop top style. The &quot;wavy pit strip&quot; description might imply some decorative detail or texture around the armpit area.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>High Waist Wide Leg Pants:</strong> These pants have a high waistline, sitting above the natural waist, and feature wide legs that flare out from the hips. They are designed to be loose and comfortable, providing a relaxed yet stylish look. The high waist can help create the illusion of longer legs and a more defined waistline.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>', NULL, NULL, 2530, 0, 0, 0, 1, 'trendy wear,summer collection,summer wear,fashionable summer wear', NULL, NULL, 'holiday-style-sling-tube-top-female-wavy-pit-strip-crop-top-high-waist-wide-leg-pants-women-fashion-two-piece-set-17106634798Xg48', 7, 0, NULL, 'Holiday Style Sling Tube Top Female Wavy Pit Strip Crop Top High Waist Wide Leg Pants Women Fashion Two Piece Set', 'trendy wea