(334, NULL, 11, 56, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Feather Sling Mesh Simple And Elegant Evening Dress', 'LD-0032', 'productImages/utpAU1710668607.jpg', NULL, 'This evening dress is a masterpiece of sophistication, blending the ethereal beauty of feather detailing with the allure of sleek mesh fabric. The design embodies simplicity and elegance, perfect for making a memorable statement at any formal event.', '<p><em>Silhouette:</em> The silhouette of this dress is sleek and form-fitting, designed to accentuate the curves of the wearer while maintaining an air of gracefulness. The bodice is structured yet lightweight, providing comfortable support and allowing for effortless movement.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Mesh Fabric:</em> Crafted from sheer mesh fabric, the dress exudes an aura of mystery and allure. The transparent nature of the mesh offers glimpses of the skin beneath, adding a touch of sensuality to the overall aesthetic. The mesh drapes delicately over the body, creating a soft and romantic silhouette.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Feather Detailing:</em> The focal point of this dress is the exquisite feather detailing adorning the neckline and straps. Each feather is meticulously placed to create a cascading effect, evoking the image of a graceful bird in flight. The feathers add a touch of whimsy and drama to the design, elevating it to a truly enchanting ensemble.</p>', NULL, NULL, 3140, 0, 0, 0, 1, 'trendy wear,summer collection,summer wear,fashionable summer wear,Gown,beatiful gown,fashionable dress,elegant party gown,stylish gown', NULL, NULL, 'feather-sling-mesh-simple-and-elegant-evening-dress-1710668607zlTQC', 7, 0, NULL, 'Feather Sling Mesh Simple And Elegant Evening Dress', 'trendy wear,summer wear,trendy summer wear,fashionable summer wear,gown,party gown,fashionable gown,elegant party gown', 'This evening dress is a masterpiece of sophistication, blending the ethereal beauty of feather detailing with the allure of sleek mesh fabric. The design embodies simplicity and elegance