(485, NULL, 38, 90, 6, 43, NULL, 'NIOR Cat Eye The Liner – Midnight Black', NULL, 'productImages/mZgyg1713856075.jpg', '[\"1713856075luaJm.jpg\"]', 'It’s pure extra-black pigments give the most intense deep black. The ultra-matte finish forbids creasing and smudging. Unique saturated ink flow makes it easy to apply and visually stunning. It can be applied on top of eyeshadow or without eyeshadow. Waterproof & smudge-proof finish that lasts all day or night.', '<p><strong>Features &amp; Details :</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Formulated Without- EDTA, Parabens, Animal Derived Raw Materials.<br />\r\n&bull; Waterproof<br />\r\n&bull; Vegan<br />\r\n&bull; Cruelty-Free<br />\r\n&bull; Maximum Lastingness up to 24 hours<br />\r\n&bull; Intense Deep Black<br />\r\n&bull; Ultra Matte Finish</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ingredient List :</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Includes high content of biodegradable and renewable natural beads made from cellulose. The vegetal beads in composition with well-known spherical fillers create this unique matte finish &amp; oil absorption. Polymeric film former maximizes great staying power &amp; water resistance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Directions :</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Place the eyeliner as close to your lash line as possible and slowly draw a thin line from the inner corner to the outer corner.<br />\r\n&bull; Keep the line thin to start. A thinner line will create a more natural look. Start at the inner corner of your eye. Some makeup artists suggest making dots or dashes along your lash line and then connecting them if you aren&rsquo;t steady while drawing a continuous line.</p>', NULL, NULL, 550, 0, 0, 100, 1, 'Nior,Nior eyeliner,Nior makeup', NULL, NULL, 'nior-cat-eye-the-liner-midnight-black-1713856075A2xh8', 6, 0, NULL, 'NIOR Cat Eye The Liner – Midnight Black', 'Nior ,Nior eyeliner,Nior makeup', 'Line along the upper lash line.', 1, 0, 0, '2024-04-23 05:07:55', '2024-06-09 07:36:04'),
(486, NULL, 38, 90, 6, 43, NULL, 'Nior Super Long Lasting Eyeliner – Black', NULL, 'productImages/FqxYI1713857873.jpg', '[\"1713857873gOdnF.jpg\"]', 'NIOR SUPER LONG LASTING EYELINER is exceptionally easy to apply. Ideal for performing precise strokes along the eyelashes. It can be used as a base shadow while creating sensual, evening smoky eyes. It can be used to underline the eye waterline without any problems. It contains a highly concentrated pigment composition giving intensive color to the eyelid.', '<p>Features &amp; Details</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Ophthalmologically Tested<br />\r\n&bull; Super Long-Lasting<br />\r\n&bull; Waterproof<br />\r\n&bull; Vitamin-Enriched<br />\r\n&bull; Cruelty-Free<br />\r\n&bull; Vegan<br />\r\n&bull; Made in Germany<br />\r\n&bull; Max Lastingness: Up to 24 hours</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Directions</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Start drawing a line from the middle of the lid along the upper lash line to the outer corner.<br />\r\n&bull; Once you have finished doing this, fill in the gap between the traced line and the lash line by moving the eyeliner pencil in light strokes.<br />\r\n&bull; From the outer corner along the lower lash line, draw a line towards the inner corner. Start drawing from the point where the line on the outer corner of the upper lash line ends.</p>', NULL, NULL, 550, 0, 0, 100, 1, 'Nior,Nior eyeliner,Nior makeup', NULL, NULL, 'nior-super-long-lasting-eyeliner-black-1713857873hx0ER', 6, 0, NULL, 'Nior Super Long Lasting Eyeliner – Black', 'Nior ,Nior eyeliner,Nior makeup', 'Line along the upper lash line.', 1, 0, 0, '2024-04-23 05:37:53', '2024-06-09 07:35:54'),
