(490, NULL, 38, 90, NULL, 43, NULL, 'Nior High Definition Ultra Defined Volume Mascara', NULL, 'productImages/o4KLC1713861645.jpg', '[\"1713861645EnGA0.jpg\"]', 'NIOR HIGH DEFINITION ULTRA DEFINED VOLUME MASCARA is highly rated for its specialty! This mascara builds, lifts, and dramatizes for sky-high lashes in a single stroke. Get full coverage for flawless fringe — this top mascara will give brilliant color and definition to every last lash. The Highly Rated Elite Mascara Brush is designed to coat lashes from root to tip. The Elite brush has a tapered end that delivers sleek, even saturation, and it combs and separates to volumize and define. Maximum volume mascara has a plant-based formula that protects and conditions without smudging, flaking, or clumping — so it’s perfect for everyday and special occasion looks.', '<p><strong>Features &amp; Details :</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Ophthalmologically Tested<br />\r\n&bull; Waterproof<br />\r\n&bull; Cruelty-Free<br />\r\n&bull; Vegan<br />\r\n&bull; Made in Germany</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ingredient List :</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Iron Oxides (77491/77492/77499), Water, Sorbitan Olivate, PPG-17/IPDI/DMPA Copolymer, Copernicia Cerifera (Carnauba) Wax, Oryza Sativa (Rice) Bran Wax, Stearic Acid, Glycerin, Hydroxyethylcellulose, VP/Hexadecene Copolymer, Sorbitol, Aminomethyl Propanol, Tocopherol, Bis-PEG/PPG-16/16 PEG/PPG-16/16 Dimethicone, Dimethicone, Isopropyl Myristate, Panthenol, Caprylic/Capric Triglyceride, Bambusa Vulgaris Leaf/Stem Extract, Phenoxyethanol, Iodopropynyl Butylcarbamate.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Directions :</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; When using maximum volume mascara for the first time, it may be necessary to prime it by pumping the brush into the container to distribute the product evenly.<br />\r\n&bull; Use the Elite brush to coat lashes from root to tip. Engage the lashes with the tapered end for a captivating curl and bold, magnetic lash color.</p>', NULL, NULL, 495, 0, 0, 100, 1, 'Nior mascara,Nior makeup,Nior', NULL, NULL, 'nior-high-definition-ultra-defined-volume-mascara-17138616453BnUP', 7, 0, NULL, 'Nior High Definition Ultra Defined Volume Mascara', 'Nior Mascara,Nior makeup,Nior', 'Experience the transformation of your lashes with the Nior High Definition Ultra Defined Volume Mascara, and enjoy bold, beautiful lashes that make a statement.', 1, 0, 0, '2024-04-23 06:40:45', '2024-06-09 07:33:57'),
(491, NULL, 38, 90, 6, 43, NULL, 'Nior On Point Micro Eyebrow Pencil – Soft Black', NULL, 'productImages/XPBwS1713862180.jpg', '[\"1713862180JeNpB.jpg\"]', 'NIOR ON POINT MICRO EYEBROW PENCIL is the perfect way to get defined and fuller-looking eyebrows. Shape and fill in your brows with this super fine tip that is capable of creating hair-like strokes. The attached spoolie helps brush and blend the color for a naturally defined look. It combs the brow hair in whatever direction you want, creating your desired brow frame. Very easy to blend & correct. Gives you a natural-looking finish all day long.', '<p><strong>Features &amp; Details :</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Precise mechanical brow liner for a defined &amp; fuller finish<br />\r\n&bull; Blend-able to a natural matte finish<br />\r\n&bull; Super thin retractable tip<br />\r\n&bull; Convenient without sharpening<br />\r\n&bull; Attached spoolie for ease of blending<br />\r\n&bull; 11-hour lastingness<br />\r\n&bull; Waterproof &amp; Vegan</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ingredient List :</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Waxes to guarantee its thin 1.7 mm lead stability. Solubilized cellulose derivates for increased lead stability and flexibility. Smooth oils like Diisostearyl Malate for even filling of gaps. Vitamin E Acetate, Argan Oil, Japanese Plum Leaf.<br />\r\nFormulated without Mineral Oil, Paraffin, Microcrystalline Wax, BHT, D4/D5/D6.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Directions :</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Shape brows with the spoolie prior to applying brow color<br />\r\n&bull; Fill your brows with hair-like strokes, and optionally draw your desired brow frame<br />\r\n&bull; Blend the brow color with the spoolie for a natural look</p>', NULL, NULL, 750, 0, 0, 100, 1, 'Nior eyebrow,Nior,Nior makeup', NULL, NULL, 'nior-on-point-micro-eyebrow-pencil-soft-black-17138621800kj7A', 7, 0, NULL, 'Nior On Point Micro Eyebrow Pencil – Soft Black', 'Nior eyebrow pencil,Nior,Nior makeup', 'The Nior On Point Micro Eyebrow Pencil in Soft Bl