(509, NULL, 38, 90, 6, 43, NULL, 'NIOR Super Long Lasting Eyeliner – Classic Nude', NULL, 'productImages/ziOY81713944350.jpg', '[\"1713944350V8HNF.jpg\"]', 'NIOR SUPER LONG LASTING EYELINER is exceptionally easy to apply. Ideal for performing precise strokes along the eyelashes. It can be used as a base shadow while creating sensual, evening smoky eyes. It can be used to underline the eye waterline without any problems. It contains a highly concentrated pigment composition giving intensive color to the eyelid.', '<p><strong>Features &amp; Details</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Ophthalmologically Tested<br />\r\n&bull; Super Long-Lasting<br />\r\n&bull; Waterproof<br />\r\n&bull; Vitamin-Enriched<br />\r\n&bull; Cruelty-Free<br />\r\n&bull; Vegan<br />\r\n&bull; Made in Germany<br />\r\n&bull; Max Lastingness: Up to 24 hours</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Directions</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Start drawing a line from the middle of the lid along the upper lash line to the outer corner.<br />\r\n&bull; Once you have finished doing this, fill in the gap between the traced line and the lash line by moving the eyeliner pencil in light strokes.<br />\r\n&bull; From the outer corner along the lower lash line, draw a line towards the inner corner. Start drawing from the point where the line on the outer corner of the upper lash line ends.</p>', NULL, NULL, 550, 0, 0, 100, 1, 'Nior,Nior eyeliner,Nior makeup', NULL, NULL, 'nior-super-long-lasting-eyeliner-classic-nude-1713944350HtNZH', 7, 0, NULL, 'NIOR Super Long Lasting Eyeliner – Classic Nude', 'Nior ,Nior eyeliner,Nior makeup', 'It contains a highly concentrated pigment composition giving intensive color to the eyelid.', 1, 0, 0, '2024-04-24 05:39:10', '2024-06-09 07:30:37'),
