(513, NULL, 38, 90, 8, 43, NULL, 'Nior On Point Micro Eyebrow Pencil – Ash Brown', NULL, 'productImages/boPgv1713955306.jpg', '[\"1713955306wIElj.jpg\"]', 'NIOR ON POINT MICRO EYEBROW PENCIL is the perfect way to get defined and fuller-looking eyebrows. Shape and fill in your brows with this super fine tip that is capable of creating hair-like strokes. The attached spoolie helps brush and blend the color for a naturally defined look. It combs the brow hair in whatever direction you want, creating your desired brow frame. Very easy to blend & correct. Gives you a natural-looking finish all day long.', '<p><strong>Features &amp; Details</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Precise mechanical brow liner for a defined &amp; fuller finish<br />\r\n&bull; Blend-able to a natural matte finish<br />\r\n&bull; Super thin retractable tip<br />\r\n&bull; Convenient without sharpening<br />\r\n&bull; Attached spoolie for ease of blending<br />\r\n&bull; 11-hour lastingness<br />\r\n&bull; Waterproof &amp; Vegan</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ingredient List</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Waxes to guarantee its thin 1.7 mm lead stability. Solubilized cellulose derivates for increased lead stability and flexibility. Smooth oils like Diisostearyl Malate for even filling of gaps. Vitamin E Acetate, Argan Oil, Japanese Plum Leaf.<br />\r\nFormulated without Mineral Oil, Paraffin, Microcrystalline Wax, BHT, D4/D5/D6.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Directions</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Shape brows with the spoolie prior to applying brow color<br />\r\n&bull; Fill your brows with hair-like strokes, and optionally draw your desired brow frame<br />\r\n&bull; Blend the brow color with the spoolie for a natural look</p>', NULL, NULL, 750, 0, 0, 100, 1, 'Herlan,Herlan makeup,Herlan eyebrow', NULL, NULL, 'nior-on-point-micro-eyebrow-pencil-ash-brown-1713955306dCvBU', 6, 0, NULL, 'Nior On Point Micro Eyebrow Pencil – Ash Brown', 'Herlan makeup,Herlan,Herlan eyebrow', 'Very easy to blend & correct. Gives you a natural-loo