(546, NULL, 11, 55, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Olive Green Tussar Silk Hand Embroidery Kantha Stitch Saree', 'I-000133', 'productImages/MbgTi1714635909.jpg', '[\"1714635909A5YuI.jpg\",\"1714635910dNWAR.jpg\",\"1714635910UK2oK.jpg\",\"1714635910GdiCz.jpg\"]', 'This exquisite saree features the timeless elegance of olive green tussar silk, adorned with intricate hand embroidery using the traditional Kantha stitch. The rich texture of tussar silk adds a luxurious touch, while the Kantha embroidery lends a unique charm with its detailed patterns and motifs. Perfect for special occasions or cultural events, this saree effortlessly combines tradition with contemporary style, making it a prized addition to any wardrobe.', '<p>The Olive Green Tussar Silk Hand Embroidery Kantha Stitch Saree is a stunning traditional Indian garment that exudes elegance and sophistication. Here&#39;s a detailed description:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Material</strong>: Tussar Silk - Known for its rich texture and natural gold sheen, Tussar silk adds a touch of luxury to any attire. It&#39;s prized for its durability and unique texture, making it a favorite choice for sarees.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Color</strong>: Olive Green - This earthy and versatile hue complements a wide range of skin tones and is perfect for both daytime and evening events. The olive green color adds a touch of subtlety and sophistication to the saree.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Embroidery</strong>: Hand Embroidery - The saree features intricate hand embroidery, showcasing exquisite craftsmanship and attention to detail. Hand embroidery adds a personalized touch to the saree, making it a unique piece of art.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Stitching Technique</strong>: Kantha Stitch - Kantha stitch is a traditional embroidery technique originating from Bengal, India. It involves simple, running stitches that create beautiful patterns and motifs on the fabric. Kantha stitch adds a rustic charm and authenticity to the saree, making it a timeless classi