(555, NULL, 11, 55, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Blue Semi Silk Cotton Saree', NULL, 'productImages/PBneJ1714885952.jpg', '[\"1714890408VRWgd.jpg\"]', 'A Blue Semi Silk Cotton Saree is a graceful blend of traditional elegance and modern comfort. Made from a mix of silk and cotton, it offers a luxurious feel with a lightweight and breathable fabric. The blue hue adds a serene and timeless charm, suitable for various occasions ranging from casual gatherings to formal events.', '<p>A Blue Semi Silk Cotton Saree typically embodies elegance with a touch of sophistication. Here&#39;s a detailed description:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Color</strong>: The primary hue is a rich shade of blue, which can vary from light sky blue to deep navy, depending on the specific design.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Fabric</strong>: The saree is crafted from a blend of semi silk and cotton. This blend combines the luxurious feel of silk with the comfort and breathability of cotton, making it suitable for various occasions and climates.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Texture</strong>: The fabric texture may vary, with the silk imparting a subtle sheen and smoothness, while the cotton adds a soft, breathable feel against the skin.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Design</strong>: The design of the saree can vary widely, ranging from traditional motifs like paisleys, floral patterns, or intricate geometric designs to more contemporary and abstract patterns. It may feature intricate embroidery, hand-painted motifs, or embellishments like sequins, beads, or zari work, adding to its allure.</p>', NULL, NULL, 500, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'Saree,Traditional Saree', NULL, NULL, 's-17148859521pLIf', 6, 0, NULL, 'Blue Semi Silk Cotton Saree', 'Saree ,Traditional Saree', 'A Blue Semi Silk Cotton Saree is a timeless wardrobe staple that seamlessly blends traditional craftsmanship with modern aesthetics, making it a cherished attire for women across various cultures and regions.', 0, 0, 0, '2024-05-05 03:12:32', '2024-05-25 02:50:02'),
