(557, NULL, 11, 55, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Green Striped Khadi Cotton Saree', NULL, 'productImages/YJc6D1714890190.jpg', '[\"1714890190LR3z0.jpg\"]', 'The Green Striped Khadi Cotton Saree is a timeless blend of traditional elegance and contemporary style. Crafted from pure khadi cotton, it boasts a rich green hue with delicate stripes running through it, adding a touch of sophistication. This saree drapes gracefully and is perfect for both casual outings and special occasions.', '<p>The Green Striped Khadi Cotton Saree is a beautiful and versatile garment that combines traditional elegance with modern simplicity. Here&#39;s a detailed description:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Material:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Khadi Cotton:</strong> Khadi is a handspun and handwoven natural fiber fabric that originated in India. It&#39;s known for its breathable and comfortable properties, making it ideal for all-day wear, especially in warmer climates.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Color and Design:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Green Base:</strong> The saree features a soothing green color as its base, evoking a sense of freshness and nature. Green is a versatile color that complements various skin tones and occasions.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Striped Pattern:</strong> The saree is adorned with fine stripes running throughout its length. The stripes add visual interest and texture to the fabric, creating a subtle yet captivating design element.</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, NULL, 500, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'Saree,Traditional Saree', NULL, NULL, 's-1714890190VE5kl', 6, 0, NULL, 'Green Striped Khadi Cotton Saree', 'Saree ,Traditional Saree', 'Despite its casual appeal, the saree can also be dressed up for more formal occasions such as office events, religious ceremonies, or social gatherings.', 0, 0, 0, '2024-05-05 04:23:10', '2024-05-25 02:49:49');
