(558, NULL, 11, 55, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Gray Striped Khadi Cotton Saree', NULL, 'productImages/256Bf1714890267.jpg', '[\"1714890267J0FVJ.jpg\"]', 'The Gray Striped Khadi Cotton Saree embodies elegance and simplicity with its understated yet sophisticated design. Crafted from lightweight khadi cotton, it offers a comfortable drape and a breathable feel, making it perfect for various occasions, from casual outings to formal gatherings. The subtle gray hue is adorned with delicate stripes, adding a touch of charm and versatility to the saree.', '<p>A Gray Striped Khadi Cotton Saree typically embodies a blend of traditional Indian craftsmanship with contemporary fashion sensibilities. Here&#39;s a detailed description:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Material:</strong> Khadi Cotton - Known for its natural texture, breathability, and comfort, Khadi Cotton is a handwoven fabric that holds a special place in Indian textiles. It&#39;s revered for its rustic charm and eco-friendliness, being spun and woven by artisans on traditional handlooms.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Color:</strong> Gray with Stripes - Gray is a versatile and sophisticated color that exudes elegance and timelessness. The addition of stripes adds a touch of modern flair while maintaining the saree&#39;s classic appeal.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Design:</strong> The saree is typically adorned with subtle, contrasting stripes running along its length, adding depth and visual interest to the fabric. The design may feature varying widths and patterns of stripes, ranging from fine pinstripes to broader bands, creating a dynamic visual effect.</p>', NULL, NULL, 500, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'Saree,Traditional Saree', NULL, NULL, 's-171489026757XI8', 6, 0, NULL, 'Gray Striped Khadi Cotton Saree', 'Saree ,Traditional Saree', 'A Gray Striped Khadi Cotton Saree is a timeless wardrobe essential that celebrates the rich heritage of Indian textiles while embracing modern design aesthetics.', 0, 0, 0, '2024-05-05 04:24:27', '2024-05-25 02:49:42'),
(559, NULL, 11, 55, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Check Printed Cotton Saree', NULL, 'productImages/wIEkx1714890309.jpg', '[\"171489030916Zfj.jpg\"]', 'A Printed Cotton Saree is a traditional Indian garment crafted from lightweight cotton fabric adorned with vibrant prints. It\'s a versatile and comfortable choice for various occasions, ranging from casual outings to formal gatherings. The intricate patterns and designs add a touch of elegance and charm to the attire, making it a popular choice among women of all ages. The breathable nature of cotton fabric makes it ideal for warm climates, ensuring comfort without compromising on style.', '<p>A Printed Cotton Saree is a traditional Indian garment crafted from lightweight cotton fabric adorned with vibrant prints. It&#39;s a versatile and comfortable choice for various occasions, ranging from casual outings to formal gatherings. The intricate patterns and designs add a touch of elegance and charm to the attire, making it a popular choice among women of all ages. The breathable nature of cotton fabric makes it ideal for warm climates, ensuring comfort without compromising on style. Whether adorned with floral motifs, geometric patterns, or intricate designs, Printed Cotton Sarees offer a timeless appeal that celebrates both tradition and modernity.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, 500, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'Saree,Traditional Saree', NULL, NULL, 's-1714890309gqtzT', 6, 0, NULL, 'Check Printed Cotton Saree', 'Saree ,Traditional Saree', 'Despite its casual appeal, the saree can also be dressed up for more formal occasions such as office events, religious ceremonies, or social gatherings.', 0, 0, 0, '2024-05-05 04:25:09', '2024-05-25 02:49:35'),
(560, NULL, 11, 55, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Pink Striped Khadi Cotton Saree', NULL, 'productImages/0wkHM1714890333.jpg', '[\"1714890334NSBwc.jpg\"]', 'The Pink Striped Khadi Cotton Saree blends tradition with contemporary elegance. Crafted from lightweight khadi cotton, it features delicate pink stripes that add a subtle charm to the classic design. Perfect for both casual and formal occasions, this saree effortlessly combines comfort with style, making it a versatile addition to any wardrobe.', '<p>The Pink Striped Khadi Cotton Saree is a stunning traditional Indian garment that exudes elegance and charm. Here&#39;s a full description:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Material:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Khadi Cotton: Khadi is a handspun, handwoven fabric that is known for its texture, breathability, and versatility. It&#39;s typically made from natural fibers like cotton, which makes it comfortable to wear in various climates.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Color:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Pink: The saree is adorned in a beautiful shade of pink, evoking a sense of femininity, grace, and sophistication. The color pink symbolizes love, compassion, and tenderness, making it a popular choice for traditional Indian attire.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Design:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Striped Pattern: The saree features a classic striped pattern, adding a touch of contemporary flair to its traditional design. The stripes run vertically along the length of the saree, creating a visually appealing and elongating effect when draped.</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, NULL, 500, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'Saree,Traditional Saree', NULL, NULL, 's-1714890334wwBFt', 6, 0, NULL, 'Pink Striped Khadi Cotton Saree', 'Saree ,Traditional Saree', 'Perfect for both casual and semi-formal occasions, this saree is a versatile wardrobe staple that can be dressed up or down depending on the event.', 0, 0, 0, '2024-05-05 04:25:34', '2024-05-25 02:49:27'),
(561, NULL, 11, 55, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Stunning Black Georgette Embellished Party Saree', 'I-000137', 'productImages/eK17k1714890462.jpg', '[\"1714890463lNvKS.jpg\",\"1714890463POO8o.jpg\",\"17148904638NqOX.jpg\"]', 'This black Georgette party saree exudes elegance and sophistication. Crafted from lightweight Georgette fabric, it drapes gracefully and offers comfort throughout the evening. The saree features intricate detailing, perhaps adorned with shimmering embellishments or delicate embroidery, enhancing its allure.', '<p>A Black Georgette Party Saree is an elegant and versatile garment perfect for various special occasions. Here&#39;s a detailed description:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Material</strong>: Georgette, a lightweight, sheer fabric made from silk or synthetic fibers, known for its flowing drape and subtle sheen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Color</strong>: Black, a timeless and classic color symbolizing sophistication and elegance. It&#39;s a versatile choice that suits various skin tones and occasions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Design</strong>:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The saree typically features intricate embellishments or embroidery along the border and pallu (the decorative end piece), adding a touch of glamour and richness.</li>\r\n	<li>It may have additional adornments like sequins, beads, zari work, or stone work, enhancing its visual appeal.</li>\r\n	<li>Some sarees may also incorporate contrasting or complementing colors in the embroidery or motifs, creating a striking contrast against the black background.</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, NULL, 4500, 3500, 0, 0, 1, 'party wear,fashionable dress', NULL, NULL, 's-1714890463KK1Ng', 6, 0, NULL, 'Stunning Black Georgette Embellished Party Saree', 'party wear,fashionable wear', 'Pair the saree with statement jewelry like chandelier earrings, a statement necklace, or bangles to enhance its glamour.', 1, 0, 0, '2024-05-05 04:27:43', '2024-06-25 07:48:55'),
