(566, NULL, 11, 55, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Black And White Polka Dots Printed Soft Chiffon Saree', 'JS1006', 'productImages/9z8IS1714899685.jpg', '[\"1714899685qZmFM.jpg\"]', 'This black and white polka dots printed soft chiffon saree effortlessly combines classic charm with modern elegance. The soft chiffon fabric drapes gracefully, offering both comfort and style. The timeless polka dot pattern adds a playful touch, while the monochromatic palette exudes sophistication. Perfect for both casual outings and formal events, this saree promises to make a chic statement wherever you go.', '<p>This black and white polka dots printed soft chiffon saree effortlessly combines elegance with a playful twist. Here&#39;s a detailed description:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Fabric:</strong> Soft chiffon, renowned for its lightweight and airy texture, ensures comfort and gracefulness, making it an ideal choice for various occasions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Color:</strong> The classic combination of black and white exudes timeless sophistication. The stark contrast creates a striking visual impact, making this saree a versatile addition to any wardrobe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Print:</strong> Polka dots, a perennial favorite in the world of fashion, adorn the saree, adding a touch of whimsy and charm. The playful pattern is balanced by the refined silhouette of the saree, making it suitable for both casual and semi-formal events.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Design:</strong> The saree features a traditional drape, with the polka dots adorning the entire length of the fabric. The black border adds definition to the saree, enhancing its overall appeal.</p>', NULL, NULL, 1250, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'Saree,Chiffon Saree', NULL, NULL, 'k-1714899685OwBZN', 8, 0, NULL, 'Black And White Polka Dots Printed Soft Chiffon Saree', 'saee,Chiffon saree', 'This black and white polka dots printed soft chiffon saree encapsulates the perfect blend of style, comfort, and versatility, making it a must-have for every fashion-conscious individual.', 0, 0, 0, '2024-05-05 07:01:25', '2024-05-25 02:49:13'),
