(568, NULL, 11, 55, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Red And Black Polka Dots Printed Soft Chiffon Saree', 'JS1004', 'productImages/452FZ1714899734.jpg', '[]', 'Elevate your elegance with this striking Red and Black Polka Dots Printed Soft Chiffon Saree. Crafted from lightweight chiffon, this saree drapes effortlessly, offering both comfort and style. The vibrant red hue is beautifully complemented by classic black polka dots, adding a timeless charm to your ensemble. Perfect for both casual and formal occasions, this saree exudes grace and sophistication with every drape.', '<p><strong>Material</strong>: Soft chiffon, a lightweight and breathable fabric known for its delicate drape and smooth texture.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Color</strong>: The saree features a striking combination of red and black, with classic polka dots printed throughout the fabric. The bold contrast between the two colors adds a playful yet elegant touch to the overall design.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Print</strong>: Polka dots, a timeless pattern, adorn the entire saree, creating a visually appealing aesthetic. The dots are evenly spaced and vary in size, adding depth and interest to the fabric.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Design</strong>: This saree is designed for versatility and sophistication. The soft chiffon material allows for graceful draping, while the red and black color scheme exudes confidence and style. The polka dot print adds a touch of whimsy, making it suitable for both casual and formal occasions.</p>', NULL, NULL, 1250, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'Saree,Chiffon Saree', NULL, NULL, 'k-1714899734Nv2UZ', 8, 0, NULL, 'Red And Black Polka Dots Printed Soft Chiffon Saree', 'saree,Chiffon saree', 'Elevate your wardrobe with this charming Red and Black Polka Dots Printed Soft Chiffon Saree, a timeless piece that combines style, comfort, and elegance effortlessly.', 0, 0, 0, '2024-05-05 07:02:14', '2024-05-25 02:48:58'),
