(637, NULL, 11, 55, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Navy Blue Tangail Madurai Half Silk Saree', 'I-000145', 'productImages/LbOwb1719034031.jpg', '[\"1719034032qn0pC.jpg\",\"1719034032699tW.jpg\",\"1719034032iSSGY.jpg\"]', 'The Navy Blue Tangail Madurai Half Silk Saree is a timeless blend of elegance and tradition, embodying the cultural richness of both Tangail and Madurai. Crafted from fine half silk, its deep navy hue exudes sophistication, complemented by intricate gold zari motifs that adorn the body and pallu. The saree\'s distinctive Madurai border, with its bold patterns and vibrant colors, adds a touch of grandeur.', '<p>The Navy Blue Tangail Madurai Half Silk Saree combines traditional craftsmanship with contemporary elegance. Handwoven in the Tangail tradition, known for its intricate motifs and lightweight texture, this saree features a rich navy blue hue that exudes sophistication. The Madurai border adds a touch of South Indian heritage with its vibrant colors and intricate patterns, complemented by a contrasting pallu that completes the ensemble with grace.</p>', NULL, NULL, 950, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'Saree,Traditional Saree', NULL, NULL, 'sare-1719034032QhFDI', 7, 0, NULL, 'Navy Blue Tangail Madurai Half Silk Saree', 'Saree ,Traditional Saree', 'Ideal for both formal occasions and cultural celebrations, this saree effortlessly blends tradition with modern style, making it a timeless addition to any wardrobe.', 1, 0, 0, '2024-06-22 03:27:12', '2024-06-27 08:57:19'),
(638, NULL, 11, 55, NULL, 44, NULL, 'Green Tangail Madurai Half Silk Saree', 'I-000146', 'productImages/lVEgP1719034078.jpg', '[\"1719034078dM2ZB.jpg\",\"1719034078BWAxw.jpg\",\"171903407821OaJ.jpg\"]', 'The Green Tangail Madurai Half Silk Saree is a graceful and elegant traditional Indian garment. It features intricate Tangail weaving, known for its fine, artistic motifs and geometric patterns. The saree is crafted from half silk, combining the richness of silk with the comfort of other fibers. Its vibrant green color adds a touch of freshness and charm, making it suitable for special occasions and cultural celebrations.', '<p>The green Tangail Madurai half silk saree combines the traditional craftsmanship of Tangail weaving with the elegance of Madurai&#39;s silk heritage. Known for its vibrant green hue and intricate patterns, this saree is a testament to the rich cultural tapestry of India. Ideal for both formal occasions and festive celebrations, it exudes grace and sophistication, making it a cherished addition to any wardrobe.</p>', NULL, NULL, 950, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'saree,cotton saree,green cotton saree', NULL, NULL, 'saree-1719034078ve3Bj', 7, 0, NULL, 'Green Tangail Madurai Half Silk Saree', 'cotton saree,green cotton saree', 'The Green Cotton Nakshi Par Saree is a beautiful blend of tradition and elegance, making it a cherished addition to any wardrobe.', 1, 0, 0, '2024-06-22 03:27:58', '2024-06-27 08:58:43'),
(639, NULL, 11, 55, NULL, 44, NULL, 'Blue Tangail Madurai Half Silk Saree', 'I-000147', 'productImages/ZCBw21719034146.jpg', '[\"1719034147WVoIg.jpg\",\"1719119255vtE7p.jpg\",\"1719119255g8QBO.jpg\"]', 'The Blue Tangail Madurai Half Silk Saree blends the traditional elegance of Madurai\'s weave with the contemporary appeal of Tangail motifs. Its half silk composition offers a luxurious drape and a lightweight feel, making it suitable for various occasions. The saree typically features intricate designs in vibrant blue hues, reflecting the cultural heritage of both Tangail and Madurai. Ideal for those who appreciate fine craftsmanship and timeless style.', '<p>The Blue Tangail Madurai Half Silk Saree is a traditional Indian garment that blends classic elegance with regional craftsmanship. Here&rsquo;s a detailed description:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Material</strong>:</p>\r\n\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li><strong>Silk</strong>: Known for its lustrous texture and durability, silk forms the base of the saree, ensuring a smooth and luxurious feel.</li>\r\n		<li><strong>Half Silk</strong>: This term typically denotes a saree where the body is made of silk, but it may also incorporate other materials like cotton or synthetic fibers in varying proportions.</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Color</strong>:</p>\r\n\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li><strong>Blue</strong>: The primary color of the saree, which can range from deep navy to lighter shades like sky blue or turquoise, adding richness and vibrancy to the garment.</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>', NULL, NULL, 950, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'Saree,Tangail saree,madrurai saree', NULL, NULL, 'saree-1719034147D1cNT', 7, 0, NULL, 'Blue Tangail Madurai Half Silk Saree', 'saree ,Tangail Half silk,madurai saree', 'This saree is a graceful choice for cultural events, weddings, and celebrations.', 1, 0, 0, '2024-06-22 03:29:07', '2024-06-27 09:00:09'),
(640, NULL, 11, 55, NULL, 44, NULL, 'Black Tangail Madurai Half Silk Saree', 'I-000148', 'productImages/CTRXg1719044886.jpg', '[\"1719044886Gmxwa.jpg\",\"1719044886syYRd.jpg\",\"17190448860LvKN.jpg\"]', 'The Black Tangail Madurai Half Silk Saree combines the intricate craftsmanship of Tangail weaving with the rich cultural heritage of Madurai silk. Known for its elegant simplicity and fine texture, this saree features traditional motifs and borders that reflect the artisanal skills of weavers from both regions. The blend of Tangail\'s lightweight cotton and Madurai\'s luxurious silk results in a saree that is both graceful and comfortable, making it a timeless choice for special occasions and celebrations.', '<p>The Black Tangail Madurai Half Silk Saree is a stunning blend of traditional craftsmanship and contemporary elegance. Crafted with half silk, it features intricate Tangail weaving, renowned for its geometric and floral motifs that adorn the body and pallu of the saree. The rich black hue enhances the allure of the saree, making it versatile for both formal and celebratory occasions. Its lightweight texture ensures comfort while draping, complemented by a contrasting border that adds a touch of sophistication. Ideal for those who appreciate timeless Indian craftsmanship with a modern twist, this saree embodies grace and cultural richness effortlessly.</p>', NULL, NULL, 950, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'cotton saree,check design', NULL, NULL, 'saree-1719044886x93UG', 7, 0, NULL, 'Black Tangail Madurai Half Silk Saree', 'cotton saree,check design', 'Pairing options include traditional jewelry such as gold or silver ornaments, depending on the occasion.', 1, 0, 0, '2024-06-22 06:28:06', '2024-06-27 09:15:25'),
