(655, NULL, 39, 95, NULL, 45, NULL, 'Branded Bag (Master Copy)', NULL, 'productImages/wwyRp1719120132.jpg', NULL, 'Type\r\nHandBags\r\n\r\nAvailable Size\r\n21 CM\r\n\r\nMagnetic-snap flap closure\r\nTop carry handle; removable, convertible shoulder strap\r\nInterior zip pocket\r\nStructured silhouette with flat base for stability\r\nLeather lining\r\nLeather\r\n\r\n1. This Small Leather Top Handle Bag is the perfect accessory for any occasion. 2. Crafted from high-quality leather, this bag is both stylish and durable. 3. The adjustable top handle and spacious interior make this bag the perfect choice for everyday use.', '<ol>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;This Small Leather Top Handle Bag is the perfect accessory for any occasion.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Crafted from high-quality leather, this bag is both stylish and durable.</li>\r\n	<li>The adjustable top handle and spacious interior make this bag the perfect choice for everyday use.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>This Small Leather Top Handle Bag has been carefully.&nbsp;crafted from the highest quality leather for an exquisite look and feel. Its top handle allows for effortless carrying and its interior dividers and pockets offer plenty of storage space for all of your everyday essentials. The timeless and sophisticated design of this bag makes it the perfect accessory to add a touch of style to any ensemble.The top zip closure ensures that all of your belongings&nbsp;are secured, while the back wall slip pocket provides quick access to your most frequently used items.This bag easily fits a small tablet, a wallet, your phone, and other smaller items. This Small Leather Top Handle Bag is the perfect accessory for any occasion. Whether you&rsquo;re heading to the office, running errands, or out for a night on the town, this bag is sure to make a statement. Its timeless design and luxurious materials make it a timeless classic that will never go out of style.</p>', NULL, NULL, 11000, 0, 0, 0, 1, 'Valentino ,Gift For Her,Handbags', NULL, NULL