(663, NULL, 39, 95, NULL, 45, NULL, 'Branded Bag (Master Copy)', NULL, 'productImages/QP6nP1719123751.JPG', NULL, 'The Dolce & Gabbana Mini Sicily Rhinestone-Embellished Top-Handle Bag (Master Copy) is a luxurious accessory that captures the brand\'s signature opulence and craftsmanship. Designed with a compact and structured silhouette, this mini version of the iconic Sicily bag is both elegant and functional. The bag is adorned with meticulous rhinestone embellishments, adding a dazzling and glamorous touch to its sleek exterior. The sparkling rhinestones are arranged in intricate patterns, enhancing the bag’s visual appeal and making it a standout piece for special occasions.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 11000, 0, 0, 0, 1, 'Handbags,ladies bag', NULL, NULL, 'bag-1719123751Ueq7G', 7, 0, NULL, 'Branded Bag (Master Copy)', 'Handbags,Ladies bag', NULL, 1, 1, 0, '2024-06-23 04:22:31', '2024-06-30 04:54:42'),
(664, NULL, 39, 95, NULL, 45, NULL, 'Branded Bag (Master Copy)', NULL, 'productImages/7y5QC1719123976.jpg', NULL, 'The Dolce & Gabbana Devotion Bag, often mimicked in high-quality replicas known as \"master copies,\" exemplifies opulent craftsmanship and distinct Italian flair. Master copies aim to closely replicate the original, emulating its luxurious design and construction. The Devotion Bag, originally launched in 2018, is renowned for its intricate detailing and high-end materials. Typically made from supple calfskin leather, it features a signature bejeweled heart emblem with a DG logo, crafted from metal and adorned with crystals and pearls.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 11000, 0, 0, 0, 1, 'Handbags,ladies bag', NULL, NULL, 'bag-1719123976kH46H', 7, 0, NULL, 'Branded Bag (Master Copy)', 'Handbags,Ladies bag', NULL, 1, 1, 0, '2024-06-23 04:26:16', '2024-06-30 04:54:56');
