(672, NULL, 39, 95, NULL, 45, NULL, 'Branded Bag (Master Copy)', NULL, 'productImages/bEPXz1719130084.jpg', NULL, 'Dolce & Gabbana\'s calfskin crossbody 3.5 bag (Master Copy) features a zipper fastening with branded slider for secure closure. It comes with an adjustable calfskin strap with light gold-plated eyelets for versatility. The bag also includes a flat calfskin pocket on the back and a calfskin interior with zipped and flat pockets for organization.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 11000, 0, 0, 0, 1, 'Handbags,ladies bag', NULL, NULL, 'bag-1719130084hetbS', 7, 0, NULL, 'Branded Bag (Master Copy)', 'Handbags,Ladies bag', NULL, 1, 1, 0, '2024-06-23 06:08:04', '2024-06-30 04:56:51'),
