(675, NULL, 39, 95, NULL, 45, NULL, 'Branded Bag (Master Copy)', NULL, 'productImages/uFuaV1719292734.jpg', NULL, 'The BVLGARI Crystal Serpenti Bag is a stunning piece of luxury fashion that blends elegance and craftsmanship. This master copy of the iconic Serpenti bag showcases the brand’s renowned artistry and attention to detail. It is inspired by BVLGARI’s celebrated Serpenti collection, characterized by its sensual curves and serpentine motifs. The bag is adorned with meticulously placed crystals, creating a shimmering effect that highlights its opulent design. The exterior often features high-quality materials like smooth leather or exotic skins, further embellished with crystals and metal accents.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 11000, 0, 0, 0, 1, 'Handbags,ladies bag', NULL, NULL, 'bag-1719130784ZrATP', 7, 0, NULL, 'Branded Bag (Master Copy)', 'Handbags,Ladies bag', NULL, 1, 1, 0, '2024-06-23 06:19:44', '2024-06-30 04:53:48'),
