(726, NULL, 38, 94, 16, 43, NULL, 'NIOR Deep Clean Gel Face Wash Soothing Menthol', NULL, 'productImages/l6oze1719726356.png', '[\"17197263567gmdH.png\",\"1719726356th547.jpg\",\"1719726356E93aG.jpg\",\"1719726356MwRqI.jpg\"]', 'Net Weight: 100ml\r\nManufacturer : Bangladesh\r\nCountry of Origin : Bangladesh', '<p><strong>Product Description</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>NIOR Deep Clean Gel Wash is an oil-free and non-comedogenic gel wash that leaves skin looking healthier, fresher, and smoother. It&#39;s unique formula cleanses deep down into the pores to dissolve dirt, oil, and make-up. It also removes dead surface skin that can make your complexion dry, rough and dull</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Features &amp; Details</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Helps to remove dirt, oil and other impurities<br />\r\nEliminates dead skin cells<br />\r\nHelps to visibly even out the skin tone</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ingredient List</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Aqua, Sodium Laureth Sulfate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Decyl Glucoside, Sodium Cocoyl Glycinate, Acrylates Copolymer, Chlorphenesin, Salicylic Acid, Vitamin B3, Phenoxyethanol, Methylchloroisothiazolinone (and) Methylisothiazolinone, menthol Extract, Color, Perfume</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Directions</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Apply a small amount to a damp face and neck and massage gently for 30 seconds. Rinse thoroughly. Use twice a day.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Deeply cleanses skin from impurities &amp; excess sebum, Refreshing &amp; smooth Skin, exfoliate dead skin cells, minimize pores &amp; improves uneven skin tone</p>', NULL, NULL, 300, 0, 0, 100, 1, 'Nior Facewash,Menthol Facewash,Nior Deep Clean Facewash', NULL, NULL, 'nior-deep-clean-gel-face-wash-soothing-menthol-1719726356LeOLk', 7, 0, NULL, 'NIOR Deep Clean Gel Face Wash Soothing Menthol', 'Nior Facewash,Menthol Facewash,Nior Deep clean Facewash', NULL, 1, 0, 0, '2024-06-30 03:45:56', '2024-06-30 06:54:42'),
