 minutes prior to sun exposure. Re-apply every 4 hours to maintain protection.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Recommended Uses For Product</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>For external use only. Avoid contact with eyes. Do not use on damaged or broken skin. In case of irritation or allergic reaction, please contact a Dermatologist.</p>', NULL, NULL, 950, 0, 0, 100, 1, 'NIOR Aqua Splash Sunscreen SPF 50 PA++++', NULL, NULL, 'nior-aqua-splash-sunscreen-spf-50-pa-1719742585G6Kyy', 7, 0, NULL, 'NIOR Aqua Splash Sunscreen SPF 50 PA++++', 'NIOR Aqua Splash Sunscreen SPF 50 PA++++', NULL, 1, 0, 0, '2024-06-30 08:16:25', '2024-06-30 08:21:26'),
(741, NULL, 38, 94, 20, 43, NULL, 'SIODIL D-Pigment SPF 100', NULL, 'productImages/8fLM01719743409.png', '[\"171974341050OxO.png\"]', 'Siodil D-Pigment SPF 100 is a unique triple-combination topical therapy for dark spots associated with moderate-to-severe facial melasma. It is a mineral-based sunscreen with SPF 100, formulated with Titanium Dioxide combined with Tocopherol and Ascorbic Acid that protects the skin against pigment (melanin) triggered by hormones or other factors. These ingredients also offer effective protection against harmful UVA and UVB rays.\r\nNet Weight: 40ml\r\nManufacturer : Product of Remark LLC, USA\r\nCountry of Origin : United States of America', '<p><strong>Features &amp; Details</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Titanium Dioxide helps protect the skin from sun damage. It is safe, reduces acne, and is photostable.<br />\r\nTocopherol prevents skin damage, restores the skin&rsquo;s natural health, and helps in evening out the skin tone and controlling hyperpigmentation.<br />\r\nAscorbic Acid can delay or entirely stop the dark spots from darkening further.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ingredient List</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Active Ingredients:</strong> TITANIUM DIOXIDE, TOCOPHEROL, AND ASCORBIC ACID</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Inactive Ingredients:</strong> WATER, BUTYLENE GLYCOL DICAPRYLATE/DICAPRATE, ISODODECANE, BUTYLOCTYL SALICYLATE, POLYGLYCERYL-2 TRIISOSTEARATE, ACRYLATES COPOLYMER, POLYGLYCERYL-3 POLYDIMETHYLSILOXYETHYL DIMETHICONE, NIACINAMIDE, SILICA, BUTYLENE GLYCOL, LAURYL POLYGLYCERYL-3 POLYDIMETHYLSILOXYETHYL DIMETHICONE, SODIUM CHLORIDE, DISTEARDIMONIUM HECTORITE, POLYGLYCERYL-2 DIPOLYHYDROXYSTEARATE, 1,2-HEXANEDIOL, ALUMINUM HYDROXIDE, PORTULACA OLERACEA EXTRACT, STEARIC ACID, PANTHENOL, TRIETHOXYCAPRYLYLSILANE, ETHYLHEXYLGLYCERIN, PROPYLENE CARBONATE, GLYCERIN, ZEA MAYS (CORN) KERNEL EXTRACT, LAUROYL LYSINE, ADENOSINE, TRISODIUM ETHYLENEDIAMINE DISUCCINATE, HELIANTHUS ANNUUS (SUNFLOWER) SEED OIL, FRUCTAN, GLUCOSE, MORINGA OLEIFERA SEED EX