(743, NULL, 11, 55, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Gray Striped Khadi Cotton Saree', NULL, 'productImages/DjwRs1719815705.jpg', '[\"1719815705WybCb.jpg\",\"17198157058abFG.jpg\",\"1719815706q3cy3.jpg\"]', 'The Gray Striped Khadi Cotton Saree embodies elegance and simplicity with its understated yet sophisticated design. Crafted from lightweight khadi cotton, it offers a comfortable drape and a breathable feel, making it perfect for various occasions, from casual outings to formal gatherings. The subtle gray hue is adorned with delicate stripes, adding a touch of charm and versatility to the saree.', '<p>A Gray Striped Khadi Cotton Saree typically embodies a blend of traditional Indian craftsmanship with contemporary fashion sensibilities. Here&#39;s a detailed description:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Material:</strong> Khadi Cotton - Known for its natural texture, breathability, and comfort, Khadi Cotton is a handwoven fabric that holds a special place in Indian textiles. It&#39;s revered for its rustic charm and eco-friendliness, being spun and woven by artisans on traditional handlooms.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Color:</strong> Gray with Stripes - Gray is a versatile and sophisticated color that exudes elegance and timelessness. The addition of stripes adds a touch of modern flair while maintaining the saree&#39;s classic appeal.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Design:</strong> The saree is typically adorned with subtle, contrasting stripes running along its length, adding depth and visual interest to the fabric. The design may feature varying widths and patterns of stripes, ranging from fine pinstripes to broader bands, creating a dynamic visual effect.</p>', NULL, NULL, 500, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'Gray Striped Khadi Cotton Saree', NULL, NULL, 'saree-1719815705J1Gkt', 7, 0, NULL, 'Gray Striped Khadi Cotton Saree', 'Gray Striped Khadi Cotton Saree', 'A Gray Striped Khadi Cotton Saree is a timeless wardrobe essential that celebrates the rich heritage of Indian textiles while embracing modern design aesthetics.', 1, 0, 0, '2024-07-01 04:35:05', '2024-07-01 08:25:23'),
