(745, NULL, 11, 55, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Deep Red Block Print Tussar Silk Saree', NULL, 'productImages/7TH0D1719815870.jpg', '[\"1719815870cHLgg.jpg\",\"1719815870vJSSW.jpg\",\"171981587065SyM.jpg\"]', 'The Deep Red Block Print Tussar Silk Saree exudes timeless elegance with its rich hue and intricate block print design. Crafted from luxurious Tussar silk, known for its natural texture and subtle sheen, this saree drapes gracefully, accentuating the wearer\'s silhouette. The deep red color adds a touch of sophistication, while the block print detailing lends an artisanal charm. Perfect for both formal occasions and cultural celebrations, this saree effortlessly blends tradition with contemporary style, making it a versatile addition to any wardrobe.', '<p>The Deep Red Block Print Tussar Silk Saree is an exquisite piece of traditional Indian attire, renowned for its elegance and timeless appeal. Here&#39;s a detailed description:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Fabric:</strong> Tussar Silk - Tussar, also known as Kosa Silk, is prized for its rich texture and natural gold sheen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Color:</strong> Deep Red - The saree features a vibrant and luxurious deep red hue, adding a touch of opulence to any occasion. Red symbolizes auspiciousness, love, and passion, making it a popular choice for weddings and festive events.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Print:</strong> Block Print - The intricate design on the saree is created using the traditional block printing technique. Skilled artisans carve intricate patterns onto wooden blocks, which are then dipped in dye and stamped onto the fabric by hand. This process results in unique and artisanal designs, each with its own character and charm.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Design:</strong> The saree may feature various traditional motifs such as floral patterns, geometric shapes, or cultural symbols, intricately arranged across the fabric. The design is often inspired by Indian heritage and craftsmanship, reflecting a harmonious blend of tradition and contemporary style.</p>', NULL, NULL, 950, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'Deep Red Block Print Tussar Silk Saree', NULL, NULL, 'saree-1719815870JPEgW', 7, 0, NULL, 'Deep Red Block Print Tussar Silk Saree', 'Deep Red Block Print Tussar Silk Saree', 'This saree is perfect for a variety of special occasions such as weddings, festivals, parties, or cultural events.', 1, 0, 0, '2024-07-01 04:37:50', '2024-07-01 07:05:16'),
(746, NULL, 11, 55, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Beautiful Orange Tangail Madurai Half Silk Saree', NULL, 'productImages/9oCcF1719815950.jpg', '[\"1719815950wP6jO.jpg\",\"1719815951vyU2C.jpg\",\"17198159510v1vP.jpg\"]', 'A stunning blend of tradition and elegance, this Tangail Madurai saree in vibrant orange is crafted from half silk. It features intricate woven patterns, showcasing a harmonious mix of Bengal\'s Tangail and Tamil Nadu\'s Madurai weaving styles. Lightweight and comfortable, this saree is perfect for festive occasions and everyday grace, bringing together the rich cultural heritage of two distinct weaving traditions.', '<p>The Beautiful Orange Tangail Madurai Half Silk Saree is a stunning blend of traditional Tangail weaving and the vibrant aesthetics of Madurai textiles. This saree is perfect for various occasions, offering a rich cultural heritage with modern elegance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>2. Fabric &amp; Weave:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Material:</strong> Half silk (a blend of silk and cotton)</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Weave:</strong> Tangail, known for its intricate handwoven designs from West Bengal.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Texture:</strong> Lightweight and soft, making it comfortable to drape and wear.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, 1250, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'Beautiful Tangail Madurai Half Silk Saree', NULL, NULL, 'saree-1719815950KyIZ7', 7, 0, NULL, 'Beautiful Orange Tangail Madurai Half Silk Saree', 'Beautiful Tangail Madurai Half Silk Saree', 'The Beautiful Orange Tangail Madurai Half Silk Saree is a versatile and elegant choice, combining the best of traditional craftsmanship with contemporary appeal.', 1, 0, 0, '2024-07-01 04:39:10', '2024-07-01 09:14:03'),
