(748, NULL, 11, 55, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Floral Printed Maroon Chiffon Saree', NULL, 'productImages/7G9op1719816103.jpg', '[\"1719816103fINUN.jpg\",\"1719816103AZZ4a.jpg\",\"17198161037bGLh.jpg\"]', 'This elegant saree features a rich maroon hue adorned with delicate floral prints, crafted from lightweight chiffon fabric. Perfect for both casual and formal occasions, it offers a graceful and timeless look that exudes sophistication and charm.', '<p>This Maroon Chiffon Saree with floral print embodies elegance and grace. Crafted from lightweight chiffon fabric, it drapes beautifully, accentuating feminine curves while providing comfort. The rich maroon hue exudes sophistication, perfect for evening soirees or special occasions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The saree features intricate floral prints that add a touch of whimsy and charm. The vibrant blooms dance across the fabric, creating a mesmerizing visual effect. The floral motifs are delicately rendered, enhancing the saree&#39;s overall allure.</p>', NULL, NULL, 1250, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'Floral Printed Maroon Chiffon Saree,Chiffon Saree', NULL, NULL, 'saree-1719816103ey4ty', 7, 0, NULL, 'Floral Printed Maroon Chiffon Saree', 'Floral Printed Maroon Chiffon Saree,Chiffon Saree', 'This Floral Printed Maroon Chiffon Saree is a versatile wardrobe staple that seamlessly blends traditional craftsmanship with contemporary style, making it a must-have for any fashion-forward woman.', 1, 0, 0, '2024-07-01 04:41:43', '2024-07-01 06:21:06');
