(749, NULL, 11, 55, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Red And Black Polka Dots Printed Soft Chiffon Saree', NULL, 'productImages/RS0kO1719816187.jpg', '[\"1719816187Bmbyv.jpg\",\"17198161881DBW6.jpg\",\"171981618858s55.jpg\"]', 'Elevate your elegance with this striking Red and Black Polka Dots Printed Soft Chiffon Saree. Crafted from lightweight chiffon, this saree drapes effortlessly, offering both comfort and style. The vibrant red hue is beautifully complemented by classic black polka dots, adding a timeless charm to your ensemble. Perfect for both casual and formal occasions, this saree exudes grace and sophistication with every drape.', '<p><strong>Material</strong>: Soft chiffon, a lightweight and breathable fabric known for its delicate drape and smooth texture.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Color</strong>: The saree features a striking combination of red and black, with classic polka dots printed throughout the fabric. The bold contrast between the two colors adds a playful yet elegant touch to the overall design.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Print</strong>: Polka dots, a timeless pattern, adorn the entire saree, creating a visually appealing aesthetic. The dots are evenly spaced and vary in size, adding depth and interest to the fabric.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Design</strong>: This saree is designed for versatility and sophistication. The soft chiffon material allows for graceful draping, while the red and black color scheme exudes confidence and style. The polka dot print adds a touch of whimsy, making it suitable for both casual and formal occasions.</p>', NULL, NULL, 1250, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'Red And Black Polka Dots Printed Soft Chiffon Saree,Polka Dots Printed Soft Chiffon Saree', NULL, NULL, 'saree-1719816187LwLbJ', 7, 0, NULL, 'Red And Black Polka Dots Printed Soft Chiffon Saree', 'Red And Black Polka Dots Printed Soft Chiffon Saree,Polka Dots Printed Soft Chiffon Saree', 'Elevate your wardrobe with this charming Red and Black Polka Dots Printed Soft Chiffon Saree, a timeless piece that combines style, comfort, and elegance effortlessly.', 1, 0, 0, '2024-07-01 04:43:07', '2024-07-01 06:46:36'),
(750, NULL, 11, 55, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Black And White Polka Dots Printed Soft Chiffon Saree', NULL, 'productImages/JzKqW1719816263.jpg', '[\"1719816263xYvCu.jpg\",\"1719816264uugoF.jpg\",\"1719816264J5wo7.jpg\"]', 'This black and white polka dots printed soft chiffon saree effortlessly combines classic charm with modern elegance. The soft chiffon fabric drapes gracefully, offering both comfort and style. The timeless polka dot pattern adds a playful touch, while the monochromatic palette exudes sophistication. Perfect for both casual outings and formal events, this saree promises to make a chic statement wherever you go.', '<p>This black and white polka dots printed soft chiffon saree effortlessly combines elegance with a playful twist. Here&#39;s a detailed description:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Fabric:</strong> Soft chiffon, renowned for its lightweight and airy texture, ensures comfort and gracefulness, making it an ideal choice for various occasions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Color:</strong> The classic combination of black and white exudes timeless sophistication. The stark contrast creates a striking visual impact, making this saree a versatile addition to any wardrobe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Print:</strong> Polka dots, a perennial favorite in the world of fashion, adorn the saree, adding a touch of whimsy and charm. The playful pattern is balanced by the refined silhouette of the saree, making it suitable for both casual and semi-formal events.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Design:</strong> The saree features a traditional drape, with the polka dots adorning the entire length of the fabric. The black border adds definition to the saree, enhancing its overall appeal.</p>', NULL, NULL, 1250, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'Black And White Polka Dots Printed Soft Chiffon Saree,Soft Chiffon Saree', NULL, NULL, 'saree-1719816263TPSaH', 7, 0, NULL, 'Black And White Polka Dots Printed Soft Chiffon Saree', 'Black And White Polka Dots Printed Soft Chiffon Saree,Soft Chiffon Saree', 'This black and white polka dots printed soft chiffon saree encapsulates the perfect blend of style, comfort, and versatility, making it a must-have for every fashion-conscious individual.', 1, 0, 0, '2024-07-01 04:44:23', '2024-07-01 06:29:06'),
(751, NULL, 11, 55, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Multicolor Soft Chiffon Saree', NULL, 'productImages/Xm0cX1719816352.jpg', '[\"1719816352tQ6mh.jpg\",\"17198163528lno7.jpg\",\"171981635294FMW.jpg\",\"1719816352WpIWO.jpg\"]', 'The Multicolor Soft Chiffon Saree embodies elegance and grace with its lightweight and flowing chiffon fabric that drapes beautifully. Its vibrant multicolor palette adds a captivating charm, perfect for any festive occasion or cultural celebration.', '<p>A multicolor soft chiffon saree is a delightful fusion of elegance and vibrancy. Here&#39;s a detailed description:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Fabric</strong>: Chiffon is a lightweight, sheer fabric known for its softness and graceful drape. It&#39;s a popular choice for sarees due to its airy feel and fluid movement.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Color</strong>: The multicolor aspect indicates that the saree incorporates a variety of hues, creating a captivating visual appeal. These colors could be harmoniously blended or arranged in a contrasting pattern, depending on the design.</p>', NULL, NULL, 1250, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'Multicolor Soft Chiffon Saree', NULL, NULL, 'saree-1719816352LucsZ', 7, 0, NULL, 'Multicolor Soft Chiffon Saree', 'Multicolor Soft Chiffon Saree', 'In summary, a multicolor soft chiffon saree is a captivating blend of grace, comfort, and style, making it a timeless addition to any wardrobe.', 1, 0, 0, '2024-07-01 04:45:52', '2024-07-01 06:24:43'),
(752, NULL, 11, 55, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Floral Printed White Soft Chiffon Saree', NULL, 'productImages/kXxth1719816437.jpg', '[\"1719816437g529d.jpg\",\"1719816437lDU0j.jpg\",\"1719816438LFjGQ.jpg\"]', 'This elegant saree features a beautiful floral print on soft white chiffon fabric. Perfect for both formal occasions and casual gatherings, it exudes grace and sophistication. The lightweight chiffon material drapes gracefully, while the floral pattern adds a touch of femininity and charm. Ideal for those who appreciate timeless elegance with a hint of romance.', '<p>Floral Printed White Soft Chiffon Saree<br />\r\n<strong>Material:</strong> Chiffon<br />\r\n<strong>Color:</strong> White with floral print<br />\r\n<strong>Design:</strong> This saree features a delicate floral print all over the soft chiffon fabric, adding a touch of elegance and femininity to the attire.</p>', NULL, NULL, 1250, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'Floral Printed White Soft Chiffon Saree', NULL, NULL, 'saree-1719816437uDrhb', 7, 0, NULL, 'Floral Printed White Soft Chiffon Saree', 'Floral Printed White Soft Chiffon Saree', 'This floral printed white soft chiffon saree is a versatile and timeless piece that adds grace and charm to your ethnic wardrobe.', 1, 0, 0, '2024-07-01 04:47:17', '2024-07-01 06:27:02'),
(753, NULL, 11, 55, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Floral Printed Blue Chiffon Saree', NULL, 'productImages/xseNF1719821506.jpg', '[\"171982150602QHr.jpg\",\"1719821506z2jbi.jpg\",\"17198215065lDd7.jpg\"]', 'This stunning floral printed blue chiffon saree seamlessly blends elegance with vibrancy. The lightweight chiffon fabric drapes gracefully, enhancing every movement. The captivating floral print in shades of blue adds a touch of femininity and sophistication. Perfect for both formal occasions and casual gatherings, this saree exudes timeless charm and modern flair.', '<p>The Floral Printed Blue Chiffon Saree is a graceful and elegant attire that embodies the beauty of traditional Indian fashion with a modern twist. Here&#39;s a detailed description:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Fabric</strong>: Crafted from high-quality chiffon fabric, this saree offers a luxurious feel and drapes beautifully, accentuating the curves of the body.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Color</strong>: The saree features a serene shade of blue, reminiscent of clear skies or tranquil waters. This color exudes calmness and sophistication, making it perfect for various occasions.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><strong>Print</strong>: Adorned with intricate floral prints, this saree adds a touch of femininity and charm. The floral motifs are delicately designed, creating a captivating visual appeal.</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ol>', NULL, NULL, 1250, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'Chiffon Saree,Floral Printed Blue Chiffon Saree', NULL, NULL, 'saree-1719821506nzs82', 7, 0, NULL, 'Floral Printed Blue Chiffon Saree', 'Chiffon Saree,Floral Printed Blue Chiffon Saree', 'The Floral Printed Blue Chiffon Saree is a stunning wardrobe staple that effortlessly combines traditional elegance with contemporary style.', 1, 0, 0, '2024-07-01 06:11:46', '2024-07-01 06:17:12'),
(754, NULL, 11, 55, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Beautiful Pink Cotton Slub Saree', NULL, 'productImages/KaPwA1719825273.jpg', '[\"1719825273Xht7y.jpg\",\"17198252742ZpaQ.jpg\",\"1719825274cKcsO.jpg\"]', 'Embrace the timeless allure of tradition with this exquisite pink cotton slub saree. Crafted from high-quality cotton, it offers a blend of comfort and elegance. The soft, slub texture enhances its graceful drape, making it perfect for both casual and festive occasions. The saree features subtle, intricate patterns that add a touch of sophistication, while its vibrant pink hue brings a fresh, lively feel to your ensemble. Complete your look with minimalistic jewelry for an effortlessly chic appearance.', '<p>This exquisite Pink Cotton Slub Saree embodies elegance and simplicity, making it a versatile addition to any wardrobe. Perfect for various occasions, from casual outings to semi-formal events, its graceful design and comfortable fabric ensure you look effortlessly chic.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Fabric &amp; Texture</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Material:</strong> 100% Cotton Slub</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Feel:</strong> Soft, breathable, and lightweight with a slightly textured finish that gives the saree a rustic yet sophisticated appearance.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Drape:</strong> The cotton slub fabric drapes beautifully, providing a natural flow that enhances the wearer&rsquo;s silhouette.</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, NULL, 700, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'Beautiful Pink Cotton Slub Saree', NULL, NULL, 'sareee-1719825273PxvHB', 7, 0, NULL, 'Beautiful Pink Cotton Slub Saree', 'Beautiful Pink Cotton Slub Saree', 'for festive celebrations, formal gatherings, or casual outings, this saree promises to enhance your wardrobe with its timeless appeal and comfort.', 1, 0, 0, '2024-07-01 07:14:33', '2024-07-01 09:24:35'),
(755, NULL, 38, 94, 19, 43, NULL, 'SIODIL Anti-Aging Serum', NULL, 'productImages/54AKh1719899834.png', '[\"1719899834aY8D2.png\"]', 'Net Weight: 30ml\r\nCountry of Origin : Bangladesh', '<p><strong>Product Description</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Siodil Anti-Aging Serum is a perfect treatment for imbalanced tone and texture, anti-aging issues, and dullness. This advanced serum, developed with a high concentration of Vitamin C and Sodium Hyaluronate, penetrates the skin to eliminate wrinkles, softens fine lines, hydrates, and boosts the skin&rsquo;s glow.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Skin Concern</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fine lines, Loss of Elasticity, Skin Damage, Wrinkles</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ingredients based benefits</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>High concentrations of Vitamin C and Sodium Hyaluronate work on the skin to eliminate wrinkles and boost the skin&rsquo;s glow.</li>\r\n	<li>Vitamin C works as an Anti-Oxidant agent that nourishes and hydrates skin and softens fine lines.</li>\r\n	<li>Sodium Hyaluronate rejuvenates the skin by improving elasticity.</li>\r\n	<li>Sodium Hyaluronate balances the pH of various skin types.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ingredient List</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>AQUA, ALOE VERA LEAF JUICE, PALMITOYL PENTAPEPTIDE-4, SHEA BUTTER, CHAMOMILE FLOWER EXTRACT, GREEN TEA LEAF EXTRACT, OLIVE LEAF EXTRACT, CARBOMER, ARGININE, ORANGE OIL, PHENOXYETHANOL, ETHYLHEXYLGLYCERINE.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Active Ingredient(s) with Percentage %</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SODIUM HYALURONATE, VITAMIN C</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Directions</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Before using heavier moisturizers, apply a pea-sized amount on a clean face.</li>\r\n	<li>Avoid direct sunlight exposure by using sunscreen during the day.</li>\r\n	<li>To be used on a daily basis in the mornings and evenings.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Product Safety</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>pH Balance</li>\r\n	<li>Cruelty-Free</li>\r\n	<li>Alcohol-Free</li>\r\n	<li>Hydration</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Disclaimer</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>This serum contains vitamin C and sodium hyaluronate as active ingredients.Please be advised that initial usage may cause irritation. To get better results, please use it for at least 2 weeks. In case of irritation or allergic reaction, please contact a dermatologist.</p>', NULL, NULL, 1590, 0, 0, 100, 1, 'SIODIL Anti-Aging Serum', NULL, NULL, 'siodil-antiaging-serum-1719899834ip5ZY', 7, 0, NULL, 'SIODIL Anti-Aging Serum', 'SIODIL Anti-Aging Serum', NULL, 1, 0, 0, '2024-07-02 03:57:14', '2024-07-02 03:57:32'),
(756, NULL, 38, 94, 19, 43, NULL, 'SIODIL Rejuvi Serum', NULL, 'productImages/DjXvu1719900127.png', '[\"17199001278q3ob.png\"]', 'Siodil Rejuvi Serum is a perfect solution for imbalanced texture, anti-aging issues, and dullness of the skin. This advanced serum, developed with 8-molecules HYA (Hyaluronic Acid), Ethyl Ascorbic Acid, and Natto Gum, penetrates the skin to eliminate wrinkles, soften fine lines, hydrate, and boost the skin’s glow.\r\nNet Weight: 30ml\r\nManufacturer : Product of Remark LLC, USA\r\nCountry of Origin : United States of America', '<p><strong>Features &amp; Details</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; 8-Molecules Hyaluronic Acid helps to replenish moisture and smooth fine lines and wrinkles.<br />\r\n&bull; Ethyl ascorbic acid improves collagen synthesis, reduces fine lines and wrinkles, and keeps the skin firm.<br />\r\n&bull; Natto Gum prevents premature aging by maintaining the skin&rsquo;s natural elasticity.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ingredient List</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Active Ingredients</strong>: 8-MOLECULES HYA, ETHYL ASCORBIC ACID, NATTO GUM</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Inactive Ingredients: AQUA, 1,2-HEXANEDIOL, 1,3-PROPANEDIOL, BUTYLENE GLYCOL, CAPRYLYL GLYCOL, CARBOMER, CHLORPHENESIN, CHONDRUS CRISPUS EXTRACT, DIPOTASSIM GLYCYRRHIZATE, DISODIUM EDTA, GLUCOSE, HYALURONIC ACID, HYDROLYZED HYALURONIC ACID, HYDROLYZED SODIUM HYALURONATE, HYDROXYPROPYLTRIMONIUM HYALURONATE, PEG-50 SHEA BUTTER, PERFLUORODECALIN, PERFLUORODIMETHYLCYCLOHEXANE, PERFLUOROHEXANE, PERFLUOROPERHYDROPHENANTHRENE, PHENOXYETHANOL, POTASSIUM HYALURONATE, SODIUM ACETYLATED HYALURONATE, SODIUM HYALURONATE, SODIUM HYALURONATE CROSSPOLYMER, SODIUM HYDROXIDE, XANTHAN GUM</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Active Ingredient(s) with Percentage %</p>\r\n\r\n<p>8-MOLECULES HYA, ETHYL ASCORBIC ACID, NATTO GUM</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Directions</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Before using heavier moisturizers, apply a pea-sized amount on a clean face<br />\r\n&bull; Avoid direct sunlight exposure by using sunscreen during the day</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&bull; Helps to replenish moisture and smooth fine lines<br />\r\n&bull; Help to keep skin firm and reduce fine lines and wrinkles.<br />\r\n&bull; Maintain the skin&rsquo;s natural elasticity.</p>', NULL, NULL, 1590, 0, 0, 100, 1, 'SIODIL Rejuvi Serum', NULL, NULL, 'siodil-rejuvi-serum-1719900127H6Ajf', 7, 0, NULL, 'SIODIL Rejuvi Serum', 'SIODIL Rejuvi Serum', NULL, 1, 0, 0, '2024-07-02 04:02:07', '2024-07-02 04:05:02'),
(757, NULL, 38, 94, 19, 43, NULL, 'Siodil Sebi Serum', NULL, 'productImages/GJz4J1719900397.png', '[\"1719900397IzRLP.png\"]', 'Siodil Sebi Serum is formulated with a high concentration of active ingredients, such as Niacinamide, Vitamin C, Hyaluronic Acid, and Anti-acne Peptide that helps reduce acne breakouts and makes the skin more smooth and hydrated.\r\nNet Weight: 40ml\r\nCountry of Origin : Bangladesh', '<p><strong>Product Description</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Siodil Sebi Serum is formulated with a high concentration of active ingredients, such as Niacinamide, Vitamin C, Hyaluronic Acid, and Anti-acne Peptide that helps reduce acne breakouts and makes the skin more smooth and hydrated. Niacinamide can reduce the overall inflammatory response, resulting in fewer pimples. Vitamin C is a natural antioxidant that helps your skin detoxify &amp; reduce the bumpy appearance Hyaluronic Acid helps to regulate sebum production and keep the skin hydrated. Anti-Acne Peptide helps to rebuild and repair damaged cells and stimulate the skin&rsquo;s natural production of collagen</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ingredient List</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Active Ingredients: Niacinamide, Vitamin C, Hyaluronic Acid, Anti-Acne Peptide</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Inactive Ingredients: Aqua,&nbsp; 1,2-Hexanediol, Acrylates C10 /30 Alkyl Crosspolymer,&nbsp; Butylene Glycol, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Capric Triglyceride, Caprylyl Glycol, Ceteareth-25,&nbsp; Cetyl Alcohol, Chlorphenesin, Chondrus Crispus Extract, Cyclopentasiloxane, Dimethicone, Dimethicone Crosspolymer, Vinyl Dimethicone Crosspolymer, Disodium Edta, Glucose,&nbsp; Glycerin,&nbsp; Glyceryl Isostearate, Glyceryl Monostearate, Sodium Hyaluronate Crosspolymer, Hydrolyzed Hyaluronic Acid, Hydrolyzed Sodium Hyaluronate, Potassium Hyaluronate, Hydroxypropyltrimonium Hyaluronate, Myristoyl Hexapeptide -5, Olive Oil, Peg/Ppg-18/18 Dimethicon, Phenoxyethanol,&nbsp; Sodium Acetylated Hyaluronate, Sodium Ascorbyl Phosphate, Sodium Hyaluronate, Sodium Polyacrylate, Trideceth- 6, Xanthan Gum</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Directions</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p># Every morning and night, apply 2&ndash;3 drops on a clean face and gently massage it in with upward, circular motions<br />\r\n# Avoid direct sunlight exposure by using sunscreen during the day</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Helps reduce acne breakouts and makes the skin more smooth and hydrated.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Recommended Uses For Product</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Oily To Acne Prone Skin</p>', NULL, NULL, 1500, 0, 0, 100, 1, 'Siodil Sebi Serum', NULL, NULL, 'siodil-sebi-serum-1719900397CHEBV', 7, 0, NULL, 'Siodil Sebi Serum', 'Siodil Sebi Serum', NULL, 1, 0, 0, '2024-07-02 04:06:37', '2024-07-02 04:07:13'),
