(759, NULL, 38, 94, 19, 43, NULL, 'SIODIL Ato Mist', NULL, 'productImages/AAev91719901172.png', '[\"1719901173TZt9E.png\"]', 'Net Weight: 180ml\r\nCountry of Origin : Bangladesh', '<p><strong>Product Description</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>SIODIL Ato Mist provides moisture and nourishment for enormous radiance in any skincare routine. Infused with Sodium Hyaluronate, Sodium PCA &amp; Dipotassium Glycyrrhizinate, this Moisturizing Mist reduces open pores, prevents cracking of the skin, and provides a refreshing and youthful look.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Skin Concern</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dry Skin, Dull skin, Large Pores, Rough Skin Texture</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ingredients based benefits</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Sodium Hyaluronate provides hydration that lasts longer in cosmetic formulations and penetrates deeply into the skin. As a humectant, it pulls moisture from the atmosphere and the skin&rsquo;s underlying layers into the epidermis and reduces open pores.</li>\r\n	<li>Sodium PCA is the sodium salt of Pyrrolidone Carboxylic Acid (PCA), also known as Pyroglutamic Acid. The skin-identical ingredient helps the face retain water and stay moisturized. It has anti-aging properties and reduces the risk of bacteria and allergen attacks on the skin.</li>\r\n	<li>Dipotassium Glycyrrhizinate can be used as a flavoring and skin conditioning agent with anti-allergic and anti-inflammatory properties. Extracted from the root of the licorice plant, Glycyrrhiza Glabra, this ingredient has soothing and dark spot-fading properties.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ingredient List</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>AQUA, 1,2-HEXANEDIOL, 1,3-PROPANEDIOL, BUTYLENE GLYCOL, CAPRYLYL GLYCOL, CELLULOSE GUM, CHLORPHENESIN,&nbsp; CHONDRUS CRISPUS EXTRACT, FRAGRANCE, GLUCOSE,&nbsp; HYALURONIC ACID, HYDROLYZED HYALURONIC ACID, HYDROLYZED SODIUM HYALURONATE, HYDROXYPROPYLTRIMONIUM HYALURONATE, PEG-40 CASTER OIL, PHENOXYETHANOL,&nbsp; POTASSIUM HYALURONATE, SODIUM ACETYLATED HYALURONATE, SODIUM HYALURONATE CROSSPOLYMER, SODIUM HYDROXIDE, XANTHAN GUM</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Active Ingredient(s) with Percentage %</p>\r\n\r\n<p>SODIUM HYALURONATE, SODIUM PCA, DIPOTASSIUM GLYCYRRHIZINATE</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Key Ingredients</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>DIPOTASSIUM GLYCYRRHIZINATE, SODIUM HYALURONATE, SODIUM PCA</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Directions</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>After cleaning, close your eyes and spritz the mist on your face</li>\r\n	<li>Don&rsquo;t rinse</li>\r\n	<li>Carry on with your regular skincare routine</li>\r\n	<li>For best results, use it twice a day</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Product Safety</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Cruelty-Free</li>\r\n	<li>Alcohol-Free</li>\r\n	<li>Non-Irritant</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Disclaimer</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>This mist contains Sodium Hyaluronate and Sodium PCA as active ingredients. Please be advised that initial usage may cause irritation, if allergic to active ingredients.</p>', NULL, NULL, 1190, 0, 0, 100, 1, 'SIODIL Ato Mist', NULL, NULL, 'siodil-ato-mist-1719901173PQ9Wf', 7, 0, NULL, 'SIODIL Ato Mist', 'SIODIL Ato Mist', NULL, 1, 0, 0, '2024-07-02 04:19:33', '2024-07-02 04:20:10'),
