sted</li>\r\n	<li>Vegan</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Disclaimer</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Stop using if there is hypersensitivity to any ingredients of the product. Avoid contact with eyes. Do not take it internally. In case of irritation or allergic reaction, please contact a Dermatologist.</p>', NULL, NULL, 1590, 0, 0, 100, 1, 'SIODIL Sebi Oil Free Lotion', NULL, NULL, 'siodil-sebi-oil-free-lotion-1719916221C5Xa1', 7, 0, NULL, 'SIODIL Sebi Oil Free Lotion', 'SIODIL Sebi Oil Free Lotion', NULL, 1, 0, 0, '2024-07-02 08:30:21', '2024-07-04 06:28:33'),
