(799, NULL, 11, 63, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Black Floral Floor Touch Gown', NULL, 'productImages/ZEKa81720083306.jpg', '[\"1720083306G7nQI.jpg\",\"1720083306819pC.jpg\"]', 'Black Floral Floor-Touch Gown\r\nThis exquisite black gown showcases a captivating floral print, merging elegance with modern flair. Designed to grace the floor with its length, it exudes sophistication and timeless charm. Perfect for formal occasions, this gown ensures you make a stunning entrance.\r\n\r\nKey Features:\r\nColor: Black with floral patterns\r\nLength: Floor-touch\r\nDesign: Full-length, floral motif\r\nIdeal For: Formal events, evening wear', '<p>The Black Floral Floor-Touch Gown is a stunning, full-length ensemble designed to make a statement. Crafted from luxurious, flowing fabric, it features a captivating black base adorned with a delicate and intricate floral print. The gown elegantly skims the floor, creating a dramatic, graceful silhouette. Its fitted bodice accentuates the waist, transitioning into a voluminous skirt that enhances movement with every step.</p>', NULL, NULL, 2500, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'Black Floral Floor Touch Gown', NULL, NULL, 'gown-1720083306fywZJ', 7, 0, NULL, 'Black Floral Floor Touch Gown', 'Black Floral Floor Touch Gown', NULL, 1, 0, 0, '2024-07-04 06:55:06', '2024-07-04 07:34:57'),
(800, NULL, 11, 63, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Flower Printed Floor Touch White Gown', NULL, 'productImages/CTEFM1720083349.jpg', '[\"1720083349OGdyw.jpg\",\"1720083349cMBR5.jpg\",\"1720087506SFmz5.jpg\"]', 'The Flower Printed Floor Touch White Gown is a beautiful and elegant attire crafted from luxurious georgette fabric. This gown gracefully extends to the floor, creating a timeless silhouette that accentuates the wearer\'s figure. The pristine white base serves as a perfect canvas for the delicate floral prints that are tastefully scattered across the gown, adding a touch of color and femininity. Georgette fabric is known for its lightweight, sheer texture, and fluid drape, making this gown both comfortable and flattering.', '<p>A Flower Printed Floor Touch White Gown crafted from premium georgette fabric is the epitome of grace and elegance. This gown features a captivating floral print that adorns the soft, flowing fabric, creating a dreamy and romantic look. The georgette material, known for its lightweight and slightly crinkled texture, ensures comfort and fluidity, allowing the gown to drape beautifully and move gracefully with every step. The full-length design touches the floor, adding a touch of sophistication, while the white background highlights the vibrant floral patterns, making it a stunning choice for both daytime events and evening soirees.</p>', NULL, NULL, 2500, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'Flower Printed Floor Touch White Gown', NULL, NULL, 'gown-1720083349wuBqk', 7, 0, NULL, 'Flower Printed Floor Touch White Gown', 'Flower Printed Floor Touch White Gown', 'Perfect for a wide range of occasions, this gown combines timeless charm with modern appeal, making it a must-have for any fashion-forward wardrobe.', 1, 0, 0, '2024-07-04 06:55:49', '2024-07-04 08:05:06'),
(801, NULL, 11, 63, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Off White Short Sleeve Floor Touch Gown', NULL, 'productImages/3Swjk1720085138.jpg', '[\"1720085139u2lRe.jpg\",\"1720085139Ur7xq.jpg\",\"1720087518mnFDf.jpg\"]', 'The Off White Short Sleeve Floor Touch Gown is an elegant blend of classic design and modern sophistication. Crafted from luxurious georgette fabric, this gown exudes a timeless appeal with its off-white hue, symbolizing purity and grace. The lightweight, semi-sheer texture of georgette lends a fluid drape that flatters the silhouette, cascading effortlessly to the floor. The short sleeves provide a modest yet stylish touch, making it suitable for both formal occasions and upscale casual events. With its floor-length design, this gown offers a graceful flow, perfect for making a memorable entrance.', '<p>The Off-White Short Sleeve Floor-Touch Gown, crafted from premium georgette fabric, exudes elegance and grace. This full-length gown features a fluid and airy silhouette, perfect for formal events or upscale gatherings. The georgette material provides a lightweight feel with a subtle sheen, enhancing the gown&rsquo;s sophisticated look. Its short sleeves add a touch of modernity while offering a comfortable fit. The floor-touching hemline creates a dramatic effect, elongating the figure and adding a sense of regal poise.</p>', NULL, NULL, 2500, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'Off White Short Sleeve Floor Touch Gown', NULL, NULL, 'g-1720085139AjIjw', 7, 0, NULL, 'Off White Short Sleeve Floor Touch Gown', 'Off White Short Sleeve Floor Touch Gown', 'The Off White Short Sleeve Floor Touch Gown in georgette is a versatile addition to any wardrobe, radiating poise and sophistication.', 1, 0, 0, '2024-07-04 07:25:39', '2024-07-04 08:05:18'),
(802, NULL, 11, 63, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Mustard Yellow Pulka Dot Printed Georgette Floor Touch Gown', NULL, 'productImages/ZciSf1720085193.jpg', '[\"17200851938Wq0t.jpg\",\"17200851940GTGN.jpg\",\"1720087949WmahW.jpg\"]', 'Elevate your wardrobe with this elegant Mustard Yellow Polka Dot Printed Georgette Floor Touch Gown. Crafted from lightweight, breathable georgette, this gown showcases a vibrant mustard yellow hue adorned with playful polka dots, creating a harmonious blend of classic and contemporary styles. Its flowing silhouette cascades gracefully to the floor, providing a dramatic yet refined presence. Perfect for both formal occasions and casual outings, this gown combines comfort with chic sophistication, making it a versatile addition to your fashion ensemble.', '<p>The Mustard Yellow Polka Dot Printed Georgette Floor-Touch Gown is a captivating blend of elegance and charm. Crafted from lightweight georgette fabric, this gown features a vibrant mustard yellow base adorned with playful white polka dots, creating a delightful and lively pattern. Its floor-length design offers a graceful silhouette, perfect for both formal and semi-formal occasions. The gown&#39;s soft, flowing texture ensures comfort and ease of movement, while the subtly flared hem enhances its elegant appeal. Ideal for making a stylish statement, this gown effortlessly combines classic polka dot nostalgia with contemporary flair, making it a versatile addition to any wardrobe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, 2500, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'Mustard Yellow Pulka Dot Printed Georgette Floor Touch Gown', NULL, NULL, 'g-1720085193LLUB1', 7, 0, NULL, 'Mustard Yellow Pulka Dot Printed Georgette Floor Touch Gown', 'Mustard Yellow Pulka Dot Printed Georgette Floor Touch Gown', 'Mustard yellow polka dot printed georgette floor-touch gown exudes timeless elegance with a playful twist.', 1, 0, 0, '2024-07-04 07:26:33', '2024-07-04 08:12:29'),
(803, NULL, 11, 63, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Ivory Printed Floor Touch Long Sleeve Gown', NULL, 'productImages/pkK371720085258.jpg', '[\"1720085259cnR2p.jpg\",\"172008525954w4V.jpg\",\"1720087980VSKaT.jpg\"]', 'The Ivory Printed Floor Touch Long Sleeve Gown typically refers to a formal or semi-formal gown made of ivory-colored fabric with a printed design. It features long sleeves and is designed to touch the floor, giving it an elegant and graceful appearance suitable for various formal occasions.', '<p>An Ivory Printed Floor Touch Long Sleeve Gown typically features the following characteristics:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Color:</strong> Ivory (off-white)</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Material:</strong> Usually made from lightweight and flowing fabrics like chiffon, silk, or satin.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Design:</strong> It may have intricate printed patterns such as floral motifs, abstract designs, or geometric patterns.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Sleeves:</strong> Long sleeves, which can be fitted or flowing depending on the style.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Length:</strong> Floor-length, meaning it extends to the floor when worn, often with a slight train at the back.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Fit:</strong> The gown is typically fitted at the bodice and waist, with a flowing skirt that allows for movement.</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, NULL, 2500, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'Ivory Printed Floor Touch Long Sleeve Gown', NULL, NULL, 'g-17200852590I8eu', 7, 0, NULL, 'Ivory Printed Floor Touch Long Sleeve Gown', 'Ivory Printed Floor Touch Long Sleeve Gown', 'These gowns are often chosen for their elegance and ability to make a statement at formal occasions while providing comfort and ease of movement.', 1, 0, 0, '2024-07-04 07:27:39', '2024-07-04 08:13:00');
