(805, NULL, 11, 63, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Soft Yellow Floor Touch Long Sleeve Gown', NULL, 'productImages/Rbb5j1720086148.jpg', '[\"1720086149EP7L7.jpg\",\"17200861493Ygaq.jpg\",\"1720089326gB1sx.jpg\"]', 'Elegantly crafted from lightweight georgette fabric, this soft yellow gown features a floor-length silhouette with long sleeves. Its flowing design and delicate texture make it an ideal choice for formal occasions or special events, combining comfort with timeless sophistication.\"', '<p>The &quot;Soft Yellow Floor Touch Long Sleeve Georgette Gown&quot; typically refers to a formal or evening gown made from georgette fabric, which is lightweight and sheer, often used in elegant and flowing designs. Here&#39;s a detailed description:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Color:</strong> Soft Yellow (a pale, light shade of yellow) <strong>Length:</strong> Floor-length (reaches down to the floor when worn) <strong>Sleeves:</strong> Long sleeves (extends to or past the wrist) <strong>Fabric:</strong> Georgette (a lightweight, sheer fabric often made from silk or synthetic fibers, known for its drape and flowy quality) <strong>Design:</strong> Typically designed for formal occasions, the gown may feature intricate detailing such as:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Waistline:</strong> May have a defined waistline or be more flowing and loose.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Embellishments:</strong> Could include embroidery, beading, or sequins for added elegance.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Silhouette:</strong> Often a flowing A-line or sheath silhouette, enhancing the fluidity of the georgette fabric.</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, NULL, 2500, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'Soft Yellow Floor Touch Long Sleeve Gown', NULL, NULL, 'g-1720086149GCZ97', 7, 0, NULL, 'Soft Yellow Floor Touch Long Sleeve Gown', 'Soft Yellow Floor Touch Long Sleeve Gown', 'Suitable for formal events such as evening parties, galas, weddings', 1, 0, 0, '2024-07-04 07:42:29', '2024-07-04 08:35:26'),
(806, NULL, 11, 63, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Purple Floor Touch Long Sleeve Gown', NULL, 'productImages/7T6bx1720087407.jpg', '[\"1720087407q0qRz.jpg\",\"1720087407jOW85.jpg\",\"1720089496snQen.jpg\"]', 'A \"Purple Floor Touch Long Sleeve Gown\" typically refers to a formal or evening dress that is long enough to touch the floor, featuring long sleeves. It suggests a garment that is elegant and suitable for formal occasions, often made from flowing or luxurious fabrics, and colored in a shade of purple, known for its association with royalty and sophistication.', '<p>A &quot;Purple Floor Touch Long Sleeve Gown&quot; typically refers to a formal or evening gown with the following characteristics:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Color</strong>: Purple, indicating a rich, regal color often associated with luxury and elegance.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Length</strong>: Floor-touching, suggesting that the gown extends to the floor when worn, providing a formal and sophisticated look.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Sleeves</strong>: Long sleeves, which can vary in style from fitted to flowing, adding coverage and elegance to the gown.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Design</strong>: The design can vary widely, but such gowns often feature intricate details like embroidery, beading, or lace to enhance their visual appeal.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Fabric</strong>: Common fabrics for such gowns include satin, chiffon, velvet, or silk, chosen for their luxurious drape and texture.</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, NULL, 2500, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'Purple Floor Touch Long Sleeve Gown', NULL, NULL, 'g-1720087407ItQfy', 7, 0, NULL, 'Purple Floor Touch Long Sleeve Gown', 'Purple Floor Touch Long Sleeve Gown', 'Typically worn to formal events such as gala dinners, weddings, or other special occasions where a formal dress code is required.', 1, 0, 0, '2024-07-04 08:03:27', '2024-07-04 08:38:16'),
(807, NULL, 11, 63, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Beautiful Floor Touch White Gown', NULL, 'productImages/nj9Vc1720087433.jpg', '[\"1720087433jP7qr.jpg\",\"1720087434k92gi.jpg\"]', 'A floor-touching white gown made from silk and net fabric exudes elegance and grace. Its combination of silk for a luxurious feel and net for delicate, sheer accents creates a striking contrast, perfect for formal occasions or weddings. The gown likely features intricate detailing such as embroidery, lace, or beading, adding to its beauty and charm. Its flowing silhouette and ethereal color make it a timeless choice for those seeking a classic yet stunning ensemble.', '<p>A beautiful floor-touch white gown typically crafted from silk and net fabric exudes elegance and sophistication. Here&rsquo;s a detailed description:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Fabric:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Silk:</strong> Known for its luxurious texture and natural sheen, silk adds a soft, smooth feel to the gown. It drapes beautifully, enhancing the overall silhouette.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Net:</strong> Often used for overlays or intricate detailing, net fabric provides a delicate and ethereal appearance. It can feature embellishments like embroidery, sequins, or lace.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Design:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Floor-Length:</strong> The gown reaches the floor, creating a dramatic and graceful look suitable for formal occasions.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Fit and Flare:</strong> The silhouette may include a fitted bodice that flares out from the waist or hips, enhancing feminine curves.</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, NULL, 2500, 0, 0, 1, 1, 'Beautiful Floor Touch White Gown', NULL, NULL, 'g-1720087433Wzsmd', 7, 0, NULL, 'Beautiful Floor Touch White Gown', 'Beautiful Floor Touch White Gown', 'Pair with delicate jewelry such as earrings and bracelets to complement the gown\'s sophistication. A clutch and heels in neutral tones can complete the ensemble.', 1, 0, 0, '2024-07-04 08:03:53', '2024-0